#   woman2 "We should be receiving the coordinates any minute, commander."
    woman2 "Deberíamos recibir las coordenadas en cualquier momento, comandante."

# game/episode014.rpy:35
translate spanish episode014_bc768e43:

#   woman "They’re taking their sweet time."
    woman "Se están tomando su tiempo."

# game/episode014.rpy:36
translate spanish episode014_a0604109:

#   woman "Every minute we’re parked out here increases the chances of detection."
    woman "Cada minuto que estamos estacionados aquí aumenta las posibilidades de detección."

# game/episode014.rpy:38
translate spanish episode014_192229a5:

#   woman2 "Our scouts haven’t reported any unusual activity yet."
    woman2 "Nuestros exploradores aún no han informado de ninguna actividad inusual."

# game/episode014.rpy:40
translate spanish episode014_fdad0e42:

#   woman "Good, let’s hope it stays that way."
    woman "Bien, esperemos que siga así."

# game/episode014.rpy:41
translate spanish episode014_c8879911:

#   woman "Years of border patrolling and suddenly the top brass is eyeing new star systems again?"
    woman "¿Años de patrullas fronterizas y de repente los altos mandos vuelven a mirar a nuevos sistemas estelares?"

# game/episode014.rpy:42
translate spanish episode014_97a5fc9c:

#   woman2 "Yes, ma’am."
    woman2 "Sí, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:43
translate spanish episode014_d9d35172:

#   woman "I fail to see why, but that’s probably the reason why I’m still commanding a boat like this and not making those decisions."
    woman "No veo por qué, pero esa es probablemente la razón por la que sigo al mando de un barco como este y no tomo esas decisiones."

# game/episode014.rpy:45
translate spanish episode014_04bfacf3:

#   woman "Fleet status?"
    woman "¿Estado de la flota?"

# game/episode014.rpy:47
translate spanish episode014_51124b17:

#   woman2 "Ready and waiting, ma’am."
    woman2 "Listo y esperando, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:49
translate spanish episode014_95c18748:

#   man "Message from the Jaculus, ma’am."
    man "Mensaje del Jaculus, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:50
translate spanish episode014_67635dd6:

#   woman "Put it through."
    woman "Pásamelo."

# game/episode014.rpy:52
translate spanish episode014_5c4a0e1e:

#   ag "Commander, you are to advance to the following coordinates immediately."
    ag "Comandante, debe avanzar a las siguientes coordenadas inmediatamente."

# game/episode014.rpy:53
translate spanish episode014_c9219d18:

#   man "Receiving coordinates."
    man "Coordenadas de recepción."

# game/episode014.rpy:54
translate spanish episode014_ce8bb998:

#   woman "Display coordinates."
    woman "Mostrar coordenadas."

# game/episode014.rpy:55
translate spanish episode014_bd7756ba:

#   man "Coordinates forwarded to your display, ma’am."
    man "Coordenadas enviadas a su pantalla, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:57
translate spanish episode014_c3d5f8ab:

#   woman "What is this?"
    woman "¿Qué es esto?"

# game/episode014.rpy:58
translate spanish episode014_814f8da1:

#   woman "Are you seeing the same thing I am?"
    woman "¿Ves lo mismo que yo?"

# game/episode014.rpy:59
translate spanish episode014_82220288:

#   woman2 "I am, ma’am."
    woman2 "Sí, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:60
translate spanish episode014_f2136061:

#   woman "Jaculus, you have sent us the coordinates of the Hawwa Cluster."
    woman "Jaculus, nos has enviado las coordenadas del Cúmulo Hawwa."

# game/episode014.rpy:62
translate spanish episode014_24556d00:

#   ag "We have."
    ag "Tenemos."

# game/episode014.rpy:63
translate spanish episode014_d3ffa386:

#   woman "The Hawwa Cluster is occupied by the Taagmar..."
    woman "La agrupación de Hawwa está ocupada por los Taagmar..."

# game/episode014.rpy:64
translate spanish episode014_0324df08:

#   ag "And your question is?"
    ag "¿Y tu pregunta es?"

# game/episode014.rpy:65
translate spanish episode014_345dec1b:

#   woman "We are to overtake this cluster and assume command?"
    woman "¿Debemos alcanzar este grupo y asumir el mando?"

# game/episode014.rpy:66
translate spanish episode014_d2900f95:

#   ag "Yes."
    ag "Sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:68
translate spanish episode014_74d756d1:

#   woman "That is an act of war, sir."
    woman "Eso es un acto de guerra, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:69
translate spanish episode014_1b3a078a:

#   woman "The Taagmar will be sure to retaliate."
    woman "Los Taagmar seguro que tomarán represalias."

# game/episode014.rpy:71
translate spanish episode014_b14954d3:

#   ag "Are you refusing to carry out a direct order, commander?"
    ag "¿Se niega a cumplir una orden directa, comandante?"

# game/episode014.rpy:72
translate spanish episode014_4e772a8e:

#   woman "No, sir."
    woman "No, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:73
translate spanish episode014_3ec3cd62:

#   woman "Just making sure we’re on the same page, sir."
    woman "Sólo me aseguro de que estamos en la misma página, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:75
translate spanish episode014_a3be9cda:

#   ag "Good."
    ag "Bien."

# game/episode014.rpy:76
translate spanish episode014_2af51227:

#   ag "Now, I don’t care how you take control of that cluster, even if you have to blow up any planet there."
    ag "Ahora, no me importa cómo tomes el control de ese cúmulo, incluso si tienes que volar cualquier planeta allí."

# game/episode014.rpy:77
translate spanish episode014_42edab9a:

#   ag "Just make sure that system is ours."
    ag "Sólo asegúrate de que ese sistema sea nuestro."

# game/episode014.rpy:79
translate spanish episode014_dc24ccea:

#   woman "Yes, sir."
    woman "Sí, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:80
translate spanish episode014_7f9faf64:

#   woman "Once we’ve asserted control over the cluster, it will be hard to defend for a longer period, sir."
    woman "Una vez que hayamos afirmado el control sobre la agrupación, será difícil defenderla durante más tiempo, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:82
translate spanish episode014_5d85c94f:

#   ag "No need to worry about that, this isn’t a long-term operation."
    ag "No hay que preocuparse por eso, no es una operación a largo plazo."

# game/episode014.rpy:83
translate spanish episode014_da27c917:

#   ag "I expect to be notified as soon as the cluster is secure."
    ag "Espero que se me notifique en cuanto el clúster sea seguro."

# game/episode014.rpy:84
translate spanish episode014_a81f7d1e:

#   woman "Of course, sir."
    woman "Por supuesto, señor."

# game/episode014.rpy:85
translate spanish episode014_5bde20c9:

#   ag "Jaculus out."
    ag "Jaculus fuera."

# game/episode014.rpy:98
translate spanish episode014_380de2e1:

#   woman2 "That place is soon to become a death trap isn’t it, ma’am?"
    woman2 "Ese lugar pronto se convertirá en una trampa mortal, ¿verdad, señora?"

# game/episode014.rpy:100
translate spanish episode014_091c4750:

#   woman "Yes, it will be once the enemy realizes we’ve occupied their territory."
    woman "Sí, lo será cuando el enemigo se dé cuenta de que hemos ocupado su territorio."

# game/episode014.rpy:101
translate spanish episode014_af77f9e2:

#   woman "But we knew what we signed up for when we joined the navy."
    woman "Pero sabíamos a lo que nos apuntábamos cuando nos alistamos en la marina."

# game/episode014.rpy:104
translate spanish episode014_20b599d9:

#   woman2 "Shall I set a course for Hawwa, ma’am?"
    woman2 "¿Pongo rumbo a Hawwa, señora?"

# game/episode014.rpy:106
translate spanish episode014_1ca70dae:

#   woman "Yes, give the order and inform the rest of the fleet."
    woman "Sí, da la orden e informa al resto de la flota."

# game/episode014.rpy:107
translate spanish episode014_67c83115:

#   woman "I’ll be in my quarters, notify me once we’re about to make the insertion into the Hawwa cluster."
    woman "Estaré en mis aposentos, avísame cuando estemos a punto de hacer la inserción en el cúmulo Hawwa."

# game/episode014.rpy:108
translate spanish episode014_f8465cf8:

#   woman2 "Very good, ma’am."
    woman2 "Muy bien, señora."

# game/episode014.rpy:114
translate spanish episode014_f60d96a3:

#   "Everyone was present on the bridge after my announcement over the ship’s intercom."
    "Todos estaban presentes en el puente tras mi anuncio por el intercomunicador de la nave."

# game/episode014.rpy:116
translate spanish episode014_eded1648:

#   c "I’d like to update you all on the journey we’re about to make."
    c "Me gustaría ponerles al corriente del viaje que estamos a punto de emprender."

# game/episode014.rpy:117
translate spanish episode014_bafdc95e:

#   c "It’s clear to me that while my father, the Confessor and maybe some other nutcases we’ve yet to hear about keep pursuing that stupid prophecy of theirs, we’ll never stop being hunted."
    c "Tengo claro que mientras mi padre, la Confesora y tal vez algún otro chiflado del que aún no sabemos nada sigan persiguiendo esa estúpida profecía suya, nunca dejaremos de ser perseguidos."

# game/episode014.rpy:118
translate spanish episode014_cc886afc:

#   c "My short career as bait for the Scolguin has further strengthened that notion."
    c "Mi corta carrera como cebo de la Scolguin ha reforzado aún más esa idea."

# game/episode014.rpy:119
translate spanish episode014_66f1352a:

#   c "So we’ll start our own investigation into this matter."
    c "Así que iniciaremos nuestra propia investigación sobre este asunto."

# game/episode014.rpy:120
translate spanish episode014_a7b185ba:

#   c "Everyone else has been operating under the advantage of having more knowledge than we do, and I aim to change that."
    c "Todos los demás han actuado con la ventaja de tener más conocimientos que nosotros, y mi objetivo es cambiar eso."

# game/episode014.rpy:121
translate spanish episode014_87ebdf8e:

#   c "Thanks to my beloved father, we know that the Scolguin potentially have more information on the prophecy."
    c "Gracias a mi querido padre, sabemos que los Scolguin tienen potencialmente más información sobre la profecía."

# game/episode014.rpy:122
translate spanish episode014_36247ce0:

#   c "While it’s very tempting to drop out of a spaceship in a vacsuit and play Scolguin bait again, Ziv might have offered us a better solution."
    c "Aunque es muy tentador bajarse de una nave espacial con un traje de vacío y volver a hacer de cebo para Scolguin, Ziv podría habernos ofrecido una solución mejor."

# game/episode014.rpy:123
translate spanish episode014_4d06d899:

#   c "Uailea, the Rhenkoy homeworld, happens to be the new home of a squadron of Scolguin."
    c "Uailea, el mundo natal de los Rhenkoy, resulta ser el nuevo hogar de un escuadrón de Scolguin."

# game/episode014.rpy:124
translate spanish episode014_f49356d9:

#   c "They’re enjoying their indefinite stay inside a jail cell, after trying to assassinate some political refugees."
    c "Están disfrutando de su estancia indefinida en una celda, tras intentar asesinar a unos refugiados políticos."

# game/episode014.rpy:125
translate spanish episode014_20b12f94:

#   c "We'll try arranging a visit with the Scolguin squadron and through them establish contact with their main fleet."
    c "Intentaremos concertar una visita con la escuadra Scolguin y a través de ellos establecer contacto con su flota principal."

# game/episode014.rpy:127
translate spanish episode014_1e7497da:

#   ki "Are we just going to visit that Rhenkoy prison and claim to be next of kin coming for a family visit?"
    ki "¿Vamos a visitar la cárcel de Rhenkoy y a decir que somos parientes que vienen a visitar a la familia?"

# game/episode014.rpy:129
translate spanish episode014_2a64892c:

#   zi "We’ll have to go through the Council of Nkoy and officially petition them."
    zi "Tendremos que pasar por el Consejo de Nkoy y hacerles una petición oficial."

# game/episode014.rpy:130
translate spanish episode014_c7e45b46:

#   zi "I have some contacts in the Council’s administration, so I have good hopes of getting us an audience."
    zi "Tengo algunos contactos en la administración del Consejo, así que tengo buenas esperanzas de conseguirnos una audiencia."

# game/episode014.rpy:132
translate spanish episode014_ef052e68:

#   c "It’s a long shot, but we’re in no way capable of taking either my father or the Confessor head-on."
    c "Es una posibilidad remota, pero no somos capaces de enfrentarnos ni a mi padre ni a la Confesora."

# game/episode014.rpy:133
translate spanish episode014_3e1375ed:

#   c "So we’re going to try and see how far this particular lead will get us."
    c "Así que vamos a intentar ver hasta dónde nos lleva esta pista en particular."

# game/episode014.rpy:134
translate spanish episode014_83f4b162:

#   c "There’s another thing I’d like to announce."
    c "Hay otra cosa que me gustaría anunciar."

# game/episode014.rpy:135
translate spanish episode014_bf6aba7e:

#   c "As you know, Vess is still being held in the brig."
    c "Como sabes, Vess sigue detenido en el calabozo."

# game/episode014.rpy:138
translate spanish episode014_236983dd:

#   c "Her pivotal role in my rescue has made me decide to release her from the brig."
    c "Su papel fundamental en mi rescate me ha hecho decidir liberarla del calabozo."

# game/episode014.rpy:139
translate spanish episode014_aeda4f05:

#   c "She’ll be under my close watch at all times."
    c "Estará bajo mi estrecha vigilancia en todo momento."

# game/episode014.rpy:141
translate spanish episode014_9d54c53f:

#   na "Are you sure that’s wise, [p_name]?"
    na "¿Estás seguro de que es prudente, [p_name]?"

# game/episode014.rpy:142
translate spanish episode014_ae1911b3:

#   na "She betrayed all of us and might do it again."
    na "Nos traicionó a todos y podría volver a hacerlo."

# game/episode014.rpy:143
translate spanish episode014_6e967d5a:

#   c "I don’t think that will happen."
    c "No creo que eso ocurra."

# game/episode014.rpy:144
translate spanish episode014_c0c92eaa:

#   c "Vess has been made very aware of the precarious situation she’s in."
    c "Vess es muy consciente de la precaria situación en la que se encuentra."

# game/episode014.rpy:145
translate spanish episode014_7b5c26d6:

#   c "She’ll be back in the brig at the slightest irregularity."
    c "Volverá al calabozo a la menor irregularidad."

# game/episode014.rpy:147
translate spanish episode014_a066f406:

#   e "I’m not sure we need to be so harsh on her."
    e "No estoy seguro de que tengamos que ser tan duros con ella."

# game/episode014.rpy:149
translate spanish episode014_b9550c26:

#   na "She put all of our lives at risk!"
    na "¡Puso todas nuestras vidas en peligro!"

# game/episode014.rpy:151
translate spanish episode014_43f829e1:

#   e "She did, and she truly feels awful about it."
    e "Lo hizo, y se siente realmente mal por ello."

# game/episode014.rpy:152
translate spanish episode014_867d7ce8:

#   e "I don’t think there’s any chance she’ll betray us again."
    e "No creo que haya ninguna posibilidad de que nos traicione de nuevo."

# game/episode014.rpy:154
translate spanish episode014_940ab8ad:

#   na "I’m not so sure about that."
    na "No estoy tan seguro de eso."

# game/episode014.rpy:155
translate spanish episode014_c11e1e88:

#   na "In any case, I think it’s a good decision to have her under guard at all times."
    na "En cualquier caso, creo que es una buena decisión tenerla vigilada en todo momento."

# game/episode014.rpy:156
translate spanish episode014_8e8f2980:

#   c "I guess that’s settled then, if there aren’t any further objections?"
    c "Supongo que está decidido, si no hay más objeciones."

# game/episode014.rpy:158
translate spanish episode014_a4fd7f1c:

#   "Nobody had anything to add, so that concluded the meeting."
    "Nadie tiene nada que añadir, por lo que se da por concluida la reunión."

# game/episode014.rpy:161
translate spanish episode014_424972d4:

#   c "She’s allowed to return to her own quarters and won’t be under guard."
    c "Se le permite volver a sus aposentos y no estará bajo vigilancia."

# game/episode014.rpy:166
translate spanish episode014_0a1a9b3d:

#   c "If anything, Vess did the things she did under duress."
    c "En todo caso, Vess hizo las cosas que hizo bajo coacción."

# game/episode014.rpy:167
translate spanish episode014_b09ff7fe:

#   c "The girl has never had a family or anyone she really felt a connection with."
    c "La niña nunca ha tenido una familia ni nadie con quien sintiera realmente una conexión."

# game/episode014.rpy:168
translate spanish episode014_813a72e8:

#   c "I believe we as a crew changed all that, and she’s willing to change her ways."
    c "Creo que nosotros como tripulación cambiamos todo eso, y ella está dispuesta a cambiar su forma de ser."

# game/episode014.rpy:170
translate spanish episode014_789e4523:

#   e "I agree."
    e "Estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode014.rpy:171
translate spanish episode014_79436891:

#   e "I’ve visited Vess in the brig a couple of times and we talked about her betrayal."
    e "He visitado a Vess en el calabozo un par de veces y hemos hablado de su traición."

# game/episode014.rpy:172
translate spanish episode014_c2a3749f:

#   e "I don’t think she did all those things because she’s evil, but because there’s something broken inside her."
    e "No creo que hiciera todas esas cosas porque sea malvada, sino porque hay algo roto dentro de ella."

# game/episode014.rpy:176
translate spanish episode014_f277b3c1:

#   e "She did and truly feels awful about it."
    e "Lo hizo y se siente realmente mal por ello."

# game/episode014.rpy:177
translate spanish episode014_f5be30d1:

#   c "I’m not saying she doesn’t need to regain our trust, but doing so confined to the brig is impossible."
    c "No digo que no necesite recuperar nuestra confianza, pero hacerlo confinada en el calabozo es imposible."

# game/episode014.rpy:178
translate spanish episode014_752abf35:

#   c "She’ll need to work hard to become a full member of our crew again."
    c "Tendrá que trabajar duro para volver a ser un miembro de pleno derecho de nuestra tripulación."

# game/episode014.rpy:180
translate spanish episode014_66c4ab86:

#   na "If you all think this is the responsible thing to do, I’m willing to give it a try."
    na "Si todos pensáis que esto es lo más responsable, estoy dispuesto a intentarlo."

# game/episode014.rpy:181
translate spanish episode014_ed5b98c2:

#   c "I guess that’s settled then, if there are no further objections?"
    c "Supongo que está decidido, si no hay más objeciones."

# game/episode014.rpy:185
translate spanish episode014_1ef21f73:

#   c "While I’m thankful for her role in my rescue, her past actions are unforgivable."
    c "Aunque le agradezco su papel en mi rescate, sus acciones pasadas son imperdonables."

# game/episode014.rpy:186
translate spanish episode014_06165d78:

#   c "She’ll remain in the brig indefinitely, but I’ve promised her that she won’t lack for any comforts."
    c "Permanecerá en el calabozo indefinidamente, pero le he prometido que no le faltará ninguna comodidad."

# game/episode014.rpy:188
translate spanish episode014_367fd8e5:

#   e "Isn’t that a little harsh, [p_name_short]?"
    e "¿No es un poco duro, [p_name_short]?"

# game/episode014.rpy:190
translate spanish episode014_f04493a8:

#   na "Harsh?"
    na "¿Duro?"

# game/episode014.rpy:196
translate spanish episode014_6fa78668:

#   na "Your compassion is admirable, Eva, but I think we should err on the side of caution."
    na "Tu compasión es admirable, Eva, pero creo que debemos pecar de precavidos."

# game/episode014.rpy:197
translate spanish episode014_d5028011:

#   c "I agree."
    c "Estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode014.rpy:198
translate spanish episode014_1db62b8a:

#   c "Does anyone object to Vess remaining in the brig?"
    c "¿Alguien se opone a que Vess permanezca en el calabozo?"

# game/episode014.rpy:200
translate spanish episode014_a2053ad7:

#   "There was a silence, even Eva didn’t have anything to add."
    "Se hizo el silencio, ni siquiera Eva tenía nada que añadir."

# game/episode014.rpy:205
translate spanish episode014_c36a41d3:

#   "Céline set course to Uailea after the crew had spread out over the ship."
    "Céline puso rumbo a Uailea después de que la tripulación se hubiera repartido por el barco."

# game/episode014.rpy:220
translate spanish episode014_2fa1ec53:

#   "A few hours after entering the Rhenkoy space, the main planet of the system came into view."
    "Unas horas después de entrar en el espacio Rhenkoy, el planeta principal del sistema apareció a la vista."

# game/episode014.rpy:222
translate spanish episode014_d7d1d0d3:

#   "Uailea promised a decidedly different landscape, if the ship’s databanks were to be believed."
    "Uailea prometía un paisaje decididamente diferente, si los bancos de datos de la nave eran creíbles."

# game/episode014.rpy:223
translate spanish episode014_a213ef3b:

#   "Rhenkoy architecture was apparently distinct enough to have garnered the attention of connoisseurs galaxy-wide."
    "Al parecer, la arquitectura Rhenkoy era lo suficientemente distinta como para haber llamado la atención de los entendidos de toda la galaxia."

# game/episode014.rpy:225
translate spanish episode014_6d11f443:

#   "Other than that, the compiler of the Bastard’s on-board guide didn’t have much to tell about the home of the Rhenkoy."
    "Aparte de eso, el compilador de la guía de a bordo del Bastardo no tenía mucho que contar sobre el hogar del Rhenkoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:238
translate spanish episode014_1c2ecf30:

#   "As soon as we docked, Ziv went out to file a formal petition with the Council of Nkoy."
    "En cuanto atracamos, Ziv salió a presentar una petición formal al Consejo de Nkoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:239
translate spanish episode014_412a04ab:

#   "Apparently, as part of the procedure, petitioners were granted temporary lodgings in the Council building."
    "Al parecer, como parte del procedimiento, se concedió a los peticionarios alojamiento temporal en el edificio del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:241
translate spanish episode014_f29c9152:

#   "The apartment we were assigned had room for two people, so it was agreed that Ziv and I would stay there and that the rest of the crew would remain on the ship."
    "El apartamento que nos asignaron tenía capacidad para dos personas, así que se acordó que Ziv y yo nos quedaríamos allí y que el resto de la tripulación permanecería en el barco."

# game/episode014.rpy:242
translate spanish episode014_17285035:

#   "Several days passed without any word from the Council."
    "Pasaron varios días sin noticias del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:247
translate spanish episode014_549ff2b5:

#   "We spent the time sight-seeing and lounging."
    "Pasamos el tiempo haciendo turismo y descansando."

# game/episode014.rpy:249
translate spanish episode014_3aceadda:

#   "Uailea’s capital turned out to be a busy metropolis, and I had trouble sleeping during the night."
    "La capital de Uailea resultó ser una metrópolis ajetreada, y tuve problemas para dormir durante la noche."

# game/episode014.rpy:251
translate spanish episode014_2ce2dc3f:

#   "Ziv didn’t seem to mind the constant stream of strange noises and flashes of light seeping in from outside."
    "A Ziv no parecía importarle el constante flujo de ruidos extraños y destellos de luz que se filtraban desde el exterior."

# game/episode014.rpy:252
translate spanish episode014_74fa2206:

#   "She appeared to be fast asleep and didn’t stir as I slipped out of bed."
    "Parecía profundamente dormida y no se movió cuando salí de la cama."

# game/episode014.rpy:254
translate spanish episode014_f9854873:

#   "Expecting a visit at any moment, I spent the first night in the apartment together with Ziv."
    "Esperando una visita en cualquier momento, pasé la primera noche en el apartamento junto con Ziv."

# game/episode014.rpy:257
translate spanish episode014_ecd2e003:

#   "There was a constant stream of strange noises and flashes of light seeping in from outside."
    "Se oían constantemente ruidos extraños y destellos de luz que se filtraban desde el exterior."

# game/episode014.rpy:258
translate spanish episode014_daeacd4a:

#   "The fact that I had opted to sleep on the floor didn’t help either."
    "El hecho de que hubiera optado por dormir en el suelo tampoco ayudaba."

# game/episode014.rpy:259
translate spanish episode014_32d65147:

#   "From what I could tell, Ziv didn’t seem to mind, as she slept deeply."
    "Por lo que pude ver, a Ziv no pareció importarle, ya que durmió profundamente."

# game/episode014.rpy:261
translate spanish episode014_96bea26b:

#   "Giving into a sudden impulse, I pulled out my tablet and started pouring over the Bastard’s diagnostics."
    "Cediendo a un impulso repentino, saqué mi tableta y empecé a revisar los diagnósticos del Bastardo."

# game/episode014.rpy:262
translate spanish episode014_805efa73:

#   "Thyia kept the ship in good shape, as there were no specific issues."
    "Thyia mantuvo el barco en buen estado, ya que no hubo problemas específicos."

# game/episode014.rpy:268
translate spanish episode014_ccaad878:

#   "Next, I checked the camera feeds."
    "A continuación, comprobé la alimentación de la cámara."

# game/episode014.rpy:270
translate spanish episode014_635babf1:

#   "It seemed that everyone had gone to bed already."
    "Parecía que todo el mundo se había ido ya a la cama."

# game/episode014.rpy:271
translate spanish episode014_f2b8fb21:

#   "One camera feed was off-limits for users with a lower clearance than mine."
    "Una de las cámaras estaba prohibida para los usuarios con un espacio libre inferior al mío."

# game/episode014.rpy:273
translate spanish episode014_4f463547:

#   "For some reason, the shipwright had deemed it necessary to install a camera in the Bastard’s head."
    "Por alguna razón, el armador había considerado necesario instalar una cámara en la cabeza del Bastardo."

# game/episode014.rpy:274
translate spanish episode014_11165bf0:

#   "Maybe the previous captain needed the ability to monitor the communal showers in the unlikely event an enemy force would enter the ship through there."
    "Quizá el anterior capitán necesitaba poder vigilar las duchas comunes en el improbable caso de que una fuerza enemiga entrara en la nave por ahí."

# game/episode014.rpy:275
translate spanish episode014_ce221dde:

#   "Lilly appeared to be in the shower, washing her hair."
    "Lilly parecía estar en la ducha, lavándose el pelo."

# game/episode014.rpy:291
translate spanish episode014_a52e70e8:

#   "I stepped out into the hallway and watched the city’s traffic flying by for a time, before getting back to bed."
    "Salí al pasillo y observé el tráfico de la ciudad durante un rato, antes de volver a la cama."

# game/episode014.rpy:297
translate spanish episode014_979ea000:

#   "After a day, when it became clear that the Council’s summons would be a long time coming, I moved back to the ship, preferring the familiar confines of the Bastard."
    "Al cabo de un día, cuando quedó claro que la convocatoria del Consejo tardaría en llegar, regresé al barco, prefiriendo los confines familiares del Bastardo."

