#   "Spying on my girlfriend didn’t feel right, especially considering the row we had earlier, so I terminated the connection."
    "Espiar a mi novia no me parecía bien, sobre todo teniendo en cuenta la bronca que habíamos tenido antes, así que corté la conexión."

# game/episode014.rpy:334
translate spanish ep014_lilly_spy_terminate_422bb152:

#   "Despite our relationship, spying on my sister didn’t feel right, so I terminated the connection."
    "A pesar de nuestra relación, espiar a mi hermana no me parecía bien, así que puse fin a la conexión."

# game/episode014.rpy:336
translate spanish ep014_lilly_spy_terminate_af6ed3cd:

#   "Despite our relationship, spying on my girlfriend didn’t feel right, so I terminated the connection."
    "A pesar de nuestra relación, espiar a mi novia no me parecía bien, así que puse fin a la conexión."

# game/episode014.rpy:341
translate spanish uailea_ziv_46aee865:

#   "When we weren't sight-seeing, Ziv and I returned to the apartment to eat and sleep."
    "Cuando no estábamos haciendo turismo, Ziv y yo volvíamos al apartamento para comer y dormir."

# game/episode014.rpy:342
translate spanish uailea_ziv_e359fc5c:

#   c "How high do you think our chances are that we'll get an answer in a few hours?"
    c "¿Qué posibilidades cree que tenemos de obtener una respuesta en unas horas?"

# game/episode014.rpy:343
translate spanish uailea_ziv_e7ca459c:

#   zi "Not very high, why do you ask?"
    zi "No muy alto, ¿por qué lo preguntas?"

# game/episode014.rpy:344
translate spanish uailea_ziv_1dc14a7e:

#   c "Well, we've seen quite a lot of the capital already, so I was thinking of a change of scenery."
    c "Bueno, ya hemos visto bastante de la capital, así que estaba pensando en un cambio de escenario."

# game/episode014.rpy:346
translate spanish uailea_ziv_e83aa875:

#   zi "Where do you want to go?"
    zi "¿Adónde quiere ir?"

# game/episode014.rpy:347
translate spanish uailea_ziv_8860a5fd:

#   c "I don't really mind, as long as we're away from prying eyes."
    c "No me importa, siempre que estemos lejos de miradas indiscretas."

# game/episode014.rpy:348
translate spanish uailea_ziv_a3b67ea0:

#   zi "I think I get what you mean."
    zi "Creo que entiendo lo que quieres decir."

# game/episode014.rpy:349
translate spanish uailea_ziv_a9616291:

#   zi "But we don't have to leave this room to achieve that."
    zi "Pero no tenemos que salir de esta sala para conseguirlo."

# game/episode014.rpy:350
translate spanish uailea_ziv_52ad38a5:

#   c "Well, last time I checked we were surrounded by glass windows."
    c "Bueno, la última vez que lo comprobé estábamos rodeados de ventanas de cristal."

# game/episode014.rpy:351
translate spanish uailea_ziv_37736691:

#   c "I'm not sure living in a greenhouse fits the definition of complete privacy."
    c "No estoy seguro de que vivir en un invernadero se ajuste a la definición de privacidad total."

# game/episode014.rpy:353
translate spanish uailea_ziv_271fee12:

#   "Ziv clapped an intricate rhythm with her hands and suddenly the glass of the windows became less transparent."
    "Ziv aplaudió con sus manos un intrincado ritmo y, de repente, los cristales de las ventanas se volvieron menos transparentes."

# game/episode014.rpy:355
translate spanish uailea_ziv_615f5acc:

#   zi "Is this more what you had in mind?"
    zi "¿Es esto más lo que tenía en mente?"

# game/episode014.rpy:356
translate spanish uailea_ziv_4f7c2a96:

#   c "I think so, yes."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:357
translate spanish uailea_ziv_22941187:

#   zi "You can't look into this room from the outside anymore."
    zi "Ya no se puede mirar a esta habitación desde fuera."

# game/episode014.rpy:358
translate spanish uailea_ziv_bf6fb2b2:

#   zi "So..."
    zi "Así que..."

# game/episode014.rpy:366
translate spanish uailea_council_dd673ded:

#   "Just when the charms of Uailea’s capital began to wear very thin, a message from the Council arrived."
    "Justo cuando los encantos de la capital de Uailea empezaban a agotarse, llegó un mensaje del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:368
translate spanish uailea_council_59bfe482:

#   "Just when the charms of Uailea’s capital began to wear very thin, Ziv messaged me that she had been contacted by the Council."
    "Justo cuando los encantos de la capital de Uailea empezaban a agotarse, Ziv me envió un mensaje informándome de que el Consejo se había puesto en contacto con ella."

# game/episode014.rpy:369
translate spanish uailea_council_9fd22a13:

#   "We were invited to visit them at our earliest convenience."
    "Nos invitaron a visitarlos lo antes posible."

# game/episode014.rpy:371
translate spanish uailea_council_d2614063:

#   "Ziv and I didn’t want to squander this opportunity and made haste towards the Council chambers."
    "Ziv y yo no quisimos desaprovechar la oportunidad y nos apresuramos hacia la sala del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:372
translate spanish uailea_council_40e7e5f6:

#   c "Do you think they'll listen to us?"
    c "¿Crees que nos escucharán?"

# game/episode014.rpy:374
translate spanish uailea_council_56706bc8:

#   zi "Yes, they will, but that might be all they do."
    zi "Sí, lo harán, pero puede que eso sea todo lo que hagan."

# game/episode014.rpy:375
translate spanish uailea_council_6b935658:

#   c "Right, so you don't have much hope?"
    c "Bien, ¿así que no tienes muchas esperanzas?"

# game/episode014.rpy:376
translate spanish uailea_council_abc83c1d:

#   zi "Well, they've granted us an audience in a very short period of time, which is rare."
    zi "Nos han concedido audiencia en muy poco tiempo, lo cual es raro."

# game/episode014.rpy:377
translate spanish uailea_council_d378ebb5:

#   c "Short period of time, but we've been here for several days?"
    c "¿Poco tiempo, pero llevamos aquí varios días?"

# game/episode014.rpy:378
translate spanish uailea_council_4d2d2bd3:

#   c "Wait, this is one of those Rhenkoy things where everything has their proper order, hierarchy and procedures?"
    c "Espera, ¿esto es una de esas cosas de Rhenkoy donde todo tiene su orden, jerarquía y procedimientos adecuados?"

# game/episode014.rpy:379
translate spanish uailea_council_800f8e61:

#   zi "Yes."
    zi "Sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:380
translate spanish uailea_council_cb9f5a86:

#   c "Like relationships?"
    c "¿Como las relaciones?"

# game/episode014.rpy:382
translate spanish uailea_council_2bae8406:

#   zi "Very much so."
    zi "Muchísimo."

# game/episode014.rpy:383
translate spanish uailea_council_f42ccee4:

#   c "Why the...{w} uh...{w} haste?"
    c "Por qué la...{w} uh...{w} ¿Prisa?"

# game/episode014.rpy:385
translate spanish uailea_council_87322771:

#   zi "I'm not sure."
    zi "No estoy seguro."

# game/episode014.rpy:386
translate spanish uailea_council_a4a3f65d:

#   zi "We'll find out once we're in the Council chambers."
    zi "Lo sabremos cuando estemos en la sala del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:388
translate spanish uailea_council_acf89076:

#   "Ziv and I walked trough the jagged archways towards the Council chambers."
    "Ziv y yo caminamos por los dentados arcos hacia las cámaras del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:389
translate spanish uailea_council_0b035ada:

#   "From what I'd seen of the architecture, the Rhenkoy sure loved grand gestures."
    "Por lo que había visto de la arquitectura, a los Rhenkoy les encantaban los grandes gestos."

# game/episode014.rpy:391
translate spanish uailea_council_ade6538b:

#   "The Council chambers were no exception."
    "La sala del Consejo no fue una excepción."

# game/episode014.rpy:392
translate spanish uailea_council_9d0261e4:

#   "The enormous room was very sparsely furnished, just one long table before a huge window overlooking the planet surface below."
    "La enorme sala estaba escasamente amueblada, con una larga mesa ante una enorme ventana que daba a la superficie del planeta."

# game/episode014.rpy:393
translate spanish uailea_council_d645c812:

#   "Four chairs were occupied with members of the Council."
    "Cuatro sillas estaban ocupadas por miembros del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:394
translate spanish uailea_council_aabf1e8b:

#   "One of the women motioned us to sit."
    "Una de las mujeres nos indicó que nos sentáramos."

# game/episode014.rpy:401
translate spanish uailea_council_ee390b3d:

#   woman "The Council is glad you have returned to Uailea, Ziv."
    woman "El Consejo se alegra de que hayas vuelto a Uailea, Ziv."

# game/episode014.rpy:402
translate spanish uailea_council_95d7508f:

#   zi "My visit is only temporary."
    zi "Mi visita es sólo temporal."

# game/episode014.rpy:404
translate spanish uailea_council_e6ca1a6c:

#   woman "Doesn't Nkoy Drugga teach us that all life is transitory and thus temporary?"
    woman "¿No nos enseña Nkoy Drugga que toda vida es transitoria y, por tanto, temporal?"

# game/episode014.rpy:405
translate spanish uailea_council_edfa0801:

#   "I groaned inwardly, this was probably going to be a very long and arduous conversation..."
    "Gemí para mis adentros, probablemente ésta iba a ser una conversación muy larga y ardua..."

# game/episode014.rpy:406
translate spanish uailea_council_90508315:

#   zi "Indeed."
    zi "En efecto."

# game/episode014.rpy:408
translate spanish uailea_council_5987b494:

#   woman2 "You have brought a human companion."
    woman2 "Has traído un compañero humano."

# game/episode014.rpy:409
translate spanish uailea_council_af7484b7:

#   zi "Yes, I have."
    zi "Sí, lo he hecho."

# game/episode014.rpy:410
translate spanish uailea_council_027dc58c:

#   zi "This is [p_name], captain of the Iron Bastard."
    zi "Este es [p_name], capitán del Bastardo de Hierro."

# game/episode014.rpy:412
translate spanish uailea_council_65b776b2:

#   arl "Welcome to Uailea, [p_name]."
    arl "Bienvenido a Uailea, [p_name]."

# game/episode014.rpy:413
translate spanish uailea_council_6d0b45c9:

#   arl "We are curious to know what you would ask of the Council?"
    arl "Tenemos curiosidad por saber qué pediría usted al Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:415
translate spanish uailea_council_8ccd5fd9:

#   c "Thank you for receiving us on short notice."
    c "Gracias por recibirnos con tan poca antelación."

# game/episode014.rpy:416
translate spanish uailea_council_d5c8df0f:

#   c "A large part of our crew originally hails from the Sovereignty."
    c "Gran parte de nuestra tripulación es originaria de la Soberanía."

# game/episode014.rpy:417
translate spanish uailea_council_9973dc56:

#   c "After experiencing the injustice and atrocities committed by the Sovereignty first-hand, we decided to leave."
    c "Tras experimentar de primera mano la injusticia y las atrocidades cometidas por el Soberano, decidimos marcharnos."

# game/episode014.rpy:418
translate spanish uailea_council_99e91611:

#   c "The Sovereignty clearly didn't agree with our decision and have been in pursuit ever since."
    c "Está claro que el Soberano no estuvo de acuerdo con nuestra decisión y nos persigue desde entonces."

# game/episode014.rpy:419
translate spanish uailea_council_640ac160:

#   c "In addition, several other entities are looking for us."
    c "Además, nos buscan otras entidades."

# game/episode014.rpy:421
translate spanish uailea_council_7bf4aa80:

#   zi "Among them a religious group attempting to retrieve Raene."
    zi "Entre ellos, un grupo religioso que intenta recuperar a Raene."

# game/episode014.rpy:422
translate spanish uailea_council_b968b6b9:

#   zi "She was my original assignment, if you recall."
    zi "Ella fue mi asignación original, si recuerdas."

# game/episode014.rpy:424
translate spanish uailea_council_2ee69574:

#   woman "We do."
    woman "Lo hacemos."

# game/episode014.rpy:425
translate spanish uailea_council_d7b55bcd:

#   woman "Are we correct in understanding you seek asylum?"
    woman "¿Estamos en lo cierto al entender que busca asilo?"

# game/episode014.rpy:427
translate spanish uailea_council_d7cfdb91:

#   c "We've been able to outsmart them so far and are confident we'll be able to do so for the foreseeable future."
    c "Hasta ahora hemos sido más astutos que ellos y confiamos en seguir siéndolo en un futuro próximo."

# game/episode014.rpy:428
translate spanish uailea_council_f11d256e:

#   c "Several of the pursuing parties are acting on information provided by third parties."
    c "Varios de los perseguidores actúan a partir de información facilitada por terceros."

# game/episode014.rpy:429
translate spanish uailea_council_1d9c849e:

#   c "Recently, we've been able to identify one of those parties as the Scolguin."
    c "Recientemente, hemos podido identificar a una de esas partes como el Scolguin."

# game/episode014.rpy:430
translate spanish uailea_council_0d72569f:

#   "That name caused a minor ripple in the calm projected by the members of the council."
    "Ese nombre causó una pequeña ondulación en la calma proyectada por los miembros del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:431
translate spanish uailea_council_38ce4839:

#   "I decided to press on to keep the Nkoy off balance."
    "Decidí presionar para mantener a los Nkoy fuera de balance."

# game/episode014.rpy:432
translate spanish uailea_council_95548926:

#   c "The Rhenkoy have had dealings with the Scolguin too, I believe."
    c "Los Rhenkoy también han tenido tratos con los Scolguin, creo."

# game/episode014.rpy:434
translate spanish uailea_council_5c3b0915:

#   woman2 "We have, yes."
    woman2 "Lo hemos hecho, sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:435
translate spanish uailea_council_381daa23:

#   c "According to Ziv, you have detained several Scolguin soldiers."
    c "Según Ziv, has detenido a varios soldados escolguines."

# game/episode014.rpy:436
translate spanish uailea_council_fdaf9b4f:

#   c "We'd like to humbly request the Council for an opportunity to question the highest-ranking soldier currently detained."
    c "Nos gustaría solicitar humildemente al Consejo la oportunidad de interrogar al soldado de más alto rango actualmente detenido."

# game/episode014.rpy:438
translate spanish uailea_council_a647ed81:

#   woman "That is a highly unusual request."
    woman "Es una petición muy poco habitual."

# game/episode014.rpy:440
translate spanish uailea_council_752b5701:

#   zi "We are aware, but make the request nonetheless."
    zi "Somos conscientes de ello, pero hacemos la petición de todos modos."

# game/episode014.rpy:442
translate spanish uailea_council_7da8d71e:

#   woman2 "What do you hope to gain by talking to the Scolguin?"
    woman2 "¿Qué espera conseguir hablando con el escolguín?"

# game/episode014.rpy:443
translate spanish uailea_council_860a216a:

#   c "So far, our pursuers have had the upper hand in their hunt, they have more resources and more information than we do."
    c "Hasta ahora, nuestros perseguidores llevan ventaja en su caza, tienen más recursos y más información que nosotros."

# game/episode014.rpy:444
translate spanish uailea_council_98d48425:

#   c "We hope to establish contact with the Scolguin and find out about their meeting with Sovereignty forces."
    c "Esperamos establecer contacto con los Scolguin y enterarnos de su encuentro con las fuerzas de la Soberanía."

# game/episode014.rpy:446
translate spanish uailea_council_44b05c64:

#   woman "How will talking to a squadron commander enable you to do this?"
    woman "¿De qué manera hablar con un comandante de escuadrón te permitirá hacerlo?"

# game/episode014.rpy:448
translate spanish uailea_council_0674a012:

#   zi "The operatives currently in Rhenkoy custody were part of a special taskforce."
    zi "Los agentes actualmente bajo custodia de Rhenkoy formaban parte de un grupo especial."

# game/episode014.rpy:449
translate spanish uailea_council_fb0b65e7:

#   zi "We have reason to believe that the operatives possess more knowledge about the Scolguin hierarchy than normal soldiers."
    zi "Tenemos razones para creer que los operativos poseen más conocimientos sobre la jerarquía Scolguin que los soldados normales."

# game/episode014.rpy:451
translate spanish uailea_council_9b87330c:

#   arl "It's also much more likely that they're conditioned to resist giving up that information under interrogation."
    arl "También es mucho más probable que estén condicionados para resistirse a dar esa información en un interrogatorio."

# game/episode014.rpy:452
translate spanish uailea_council_ddbfcb96:

#   c "We are aware, but the only other way to contact the Scolguin is to offer them a live sacrifice, which we're unwilling to perform."
    c "Somos conscientes de ello, pero la única forma de contactar con los escolguines es ofrecerles un sacrificio en vivo, algo que no estamos dispuestos a hacer."

# game/episode014.rpy:454
translate spanish uailea_council_ed361d00:

#   "The Council members exchanged meaningful glances before one of the women spoke again."
    "Los miembros del Consejo intercambiaron miradas significativas antes de que una de las mujeres volviera a hablar."

# game/episode014.rpy:456
translate spanish uailea_council_cb58c1d7:

#   woman "We thank you for your petition, the Council will now deliberate in private."
    woman "Le agradecemos su petición, el Consejo deliberará ahora en privado."

# game/episode014.rpy:457
translate spanish uailea_council_fdf9d3b2:

#   woman "Please wait in the antechamber until we notify you of our decision."
    woman "Por favor, espere en la antesala hasta que le notifiquemos nuestra decisión."

# game/episode014.rpy:459
translate spanish uailea_council_1a036681:

#   "One of the doors opened behind us, prompting Ziv and I to leave the Council chambers."
    "Una de las puertas se abrió detrás de nosotros, lo que nos hizo salir a Ziv y a mí de la sala del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:461
translate spanish uailea_council_d0c9df71:

#   c "They're going to deny our request, aren't they?"
    c "Van a denegar nuestra petición, ¿no?"

# game/episode014.rpy:462
translate spanish uailea_council_feb632cc:

#   zi "Yes, that seems likely."
    zi "Sí, eso parece probable."

# game/episode014.rpy:463
translate spanish uailea_council_bb71ec58:

#   c "It was a long shot anyway."
    c "De todos modos, era una posibilidad remota."

# game/episode014.rpy:465
translate spanish uailea_council_6a5bf9bb:

#   zi "Yes, unfortunately."
    zi "Sí, por desgracia."

# game/episode014.rpy:466
translate spanish uailea_council_ee411530:

#   zi "At least the Council seems to confirm the Scolguin are still captive on Uailea."
    zi "Al menos el Consejo parece confirmar que los Scolguin siguen cautivos en Uailea."

# game/episode014.rpy:468
translate spanish uailea_council_d5695519:

#   "The Council took a good while to come to a decision."
    "El Consejo tardó un buen rato en tomar una decisión."

# game/episode014.rpy:470
translate spanish uailea_council_d16c9d12:

#   "The door slid open again after little over an hour."
    "La puerta volvió a abrirse al cabo de poco más de una hora."

# game/episode014.rpy:472
translate spanish uailea_council_a9a3b9c3:

#   arl "Welcome back."
    arl "Bienvenido de nuevo."

# game/episode014.rpy:474
translate spanish uailea_council_517a3996:

#   woman "The Council of Nkoy has reached a decision regarding your request to interview the Scolguin prisoners."
    woman "El Consejo de Nkoy ha tomado una decisión sobre su solicitud de entrevistar a los presos escolguines."

# game/episode014.rpy:475
translate spanish uailea_council_3b6833c4:

#   woman "I'm afraid we have to deny your request."
    woman "Me temo que tenemos que denegar su solicitud."

# game/episode014.rpy:476
translate spanish uailea_council_690344b1:

#   c "That's disappointing news."
    c "Es una noticia decepcionante."

# game/episode014.rpy:477
translate spanish uailea_council_2c787016:

#   c "Regardless, thank you for allowing us to petition the Council."
    c "En cualquier caso, gracias por permitirnos presentar una petición al Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:479
translate spanish uailea_council_06bd09d8:

#   woman2 "I hope your stay on Uailea is a pleasant one."
    woman2 "Espero que su estancia en Uailea sea agradable."

# game/episode014.rpy:480
translate spanish uailea_council_e27ad33e:

#   woman2 "This session of the Council of Nkoy is hereby concluded."
    woman2 "Se da por concluida esta sesión del Consejo de Nkoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:482
translate spanish uailea_council_4dc2627a:

#   "One by one, the members of the Council left the room, leaving us alone in their chambers."
    "Uno a uno, los miembros del Consejo abandonaron la sala, dejándonos solos en su despacho."

# game/episode014.rpy:484
translate spanish uailea_council_8d588c13:

#   c "A failure, like we expected."
    c "Un fracaso, como esperábamos."

# game/episode014.rpy:485
translate spanish uailea_council_8a755e69:

#   c "Not sure what we're to do now..."
    c "No sé qué vamos a hacer ahora..."

# game/episode014.rpy:486
translate spanish uailea_council_8551c5f0:

#   c "I'll message Céline to get the Bastard ready for take-off."
    c "Le enviaré un mensaje a Céline para que prepare al Bastardo para despegar."

# game/episode014.rpy:488
translate spanish uailea_council_155b02ff:

#   zi "Let's hold off on that for a few hours."
    zi "Dejemos eso para dentro de unas horas."

# game/episode014.rpy:489
translate spanish uailea_council_4e5a4202:

#   c "Why?"
    c "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode014.rpy:490
translate spanish uailea_council_83a97635:

#   zi "If I'm not mistaken, Nkoy Arlya gave me a signal just before she left the Council chambers."
    zi "Si no me equivoco, Nkoy Arlya me hizo una señal justo antes de abandonar la sala del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:491
translate spanish uailea_council_60f6899f:

#   c "A signal?"
    c "¿Una señal?"

# game/episode014.rpy:493
translate spanish uailea_council_367924cd:

#   zi "I have a feeling she wants to talk to us in private."
    zi "Tengo la sensación de que quiere hablar con nosotros en privado."

# game/episode014.rpy:494
translate spanish uailea_council_18bf4077:

#   c "Let's wait for her, in that case."
    c "Esperémosla, en ese caso."

# game/episode014.rpy:496
translate spanish uailea_council_83f1a9d5:

#   "Considering Ziv's suspicions, I was half expecting Nkoy Arlya already waiting on us in Ziv's chambers."
    "Teniendo en cuenta las sospechas de Ziv, medio esperaba que Nkoy Arlya ya nos estuviera esperando en los aposentos de Ziv."

# game/episode014.rpy:498
translate spanish uailea_council_2028cbeb:

#   "The room was empty, however."
    "Sin embargo, la habitación estaba vacía."

# game/episode014.rpy:500
translate spanish uailea_council_35fa45ce:

#   "Ziv and I made ourselves comfortable and waited on Arlya's arrival."
    "Ziv y yo nos pusimos cómodos y esperamos la llegada de Arlya."

# game/episode014.rpy:501
translate spanish uailea_council_1eacdec4:

#   "After several hours I began to think Ziv had been mistaken about the signal and no one was coming."
    "Después de varias horas empecé a pensar que Ziv se había equivocado con la señal y que no venía nadie."

# game/episode014.rpy:503
translate spanish uailea_council_c7648479:

#   "Just when I was about to voice my thoughts, somebody pressed the door buzzer."
    "Justo cuando iba a expresar mis pensamientos, alguien pulsó el timbre de la puerta."

# game/episode014.rpy:505
translate spanish uailea_council_a5bfc2c3:

#   "Ziv opened the door and Nkoy Arlya stepped inside."
    "Ziv abrió la puerta y Nkoy Arlya entró."

# game/episode014.rpy:507
translate spanish uailea_council_92c45131:

#   "Before uttering a word, she immediately gave the command to turn the windows opaque."
    "Antes de pronunciar una palabra, dio inmediatamente la orden de volver opacas las ventanas."

# game/episode014.rpy:510
translate spanish uailea_council_49898726:

#   arl "I'm sorry about that and to have kept you waiting for so long."
    arl "Lo siento por eso y por haberte hecho esperar tanto tiempo."

# game/episode014.rpy:511
translate spanish uailea_council_f2137082:

#   arl "I'd like to keep this meeting private, and I've been tied up in business for the past few hours."
    arl "Me gustaría mantener esta reunión en privado, y he estado ocupado en negocios durante las últimas horas."

# game/episode014.rpy:513
translate spanish uailea_council_5ba57dad:

#   zi "You are welcome all the same, Nkoy Arlya."
    zi "De nada, Nkoy Arlya."

# game/episode014.rpy:515
translate spanish uailea_council_f22f27bf:

#   arl "Just Arlya is enough, thank you."
    arl "Con Arlya es suficiente, gracias."

# game/episode014.rpy:517
translate spanish uailea_council_6d5491a8:

#   arl "I won't waste your time with any niceties and just cut right to heart of the matter."
    arl "No voy a hacerle perder el tiempo con sutilezas y voy a ir directamente al meollo de la cuestión."

# game/episode014.rpy:518
translate spanish uailea_council_8cb9a804:

#   arl "The Council has rejected your request, but I may be able to grant you access to the prisoners."
    arl "El Consejo ha rechazado su petición, pero quizá pueda concederle acceso a los prisioneros."

# game/episode014.rpy:519
translate spanish uailea_council_b99dd49c:

#   arl "I'm sure you're shocked Ziv, because this goes expressly against the Council's verdict."
    arl "Estoy seguro de que estás conmocionado Ziv, porque esto va expresamente en contra del veredicto del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:521
translate spanish uailea_council_13274057:

#   zi "Shocked is too big a word, but I must admit I'm surprised you're willing to go against the Council's wishes."
    zi "Sorprendido es una palabra demasiado grande, pero debo admitir que me sorprende que estés dispuesto a ir en contra de los deseos del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:523
translate spanish uailea_council_5a1f7cee:

#   arl "I wouldn't normally, but certain events have forced my hand."
    arl "Normalmente no lo haría, pero ciertos acontecimientos me han obligado a ello."

# game/episode014.rpy:524
translate spanish uailea_council_a5f73143:

#   arl "To be clear, I expect something in return for allowing you access to the prisoners."
    arl "Para ser claro, espero algo a cambio de permitirle el acceso a los prisioneros."

# game/episode014.rpy:525
translate spanish uailea_council_99a88f33:

#   c "I reckoned as much."
    c "Me lo imaginaba."

# game/episode014.rpy:526
translate spanish uailea_council_d8cbdd56:

#   arl "It's a delicate matter that I'd rather want handled by people outside the Rhenkoy."
    arl "Es un asunto delicado que preferiría que se encargara gente ajena al Rhenkoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:527
translate spanish uailea_council_656a7ac7:

#   arl "Your ties to Rhenkoy politics are tenuous at best, Ziv, if I'm not mistaken?"
    arl "Tus vínculos con la política Rhenkoy son tenues en el mejor de los casos, Ziv, si no me equivoco."

# game/episode014.rpy:528
translate spanish uailea_council_77693289:

#   zi "I've been away for quite some time."
    zi "He estado fuera bastante tiempo."

# game/episode014.rpy:530
translate spanish uailea_council_0ad21fae:

#   arl "Exactly."
    arl "Exactamente."

# game/episode014.rpy:532
translate spanish uailea_council_4038e737:

#   arl "Before I continue, do I have your oath that you will talk about this with no one else?"
    arl "Antes de continuar, ¿tengo tu juramento de que no hablarás de esto con nadie más?"

# game/episode014.rpy:533
translate spanish uailea_council_b337f098:

#   "I looked at Ziv, who nodded slightly."
    "Miré a Ziv, que asintió levemente."

# game/episode014.rpy:534
translate spanish uailea_council_99a553be:

#   c "You have our word."
    c "Tienes nuestra palabra."

# game/episode014.rpy:536
translate spanish uailea_council_b069e9d8:

#   arl "Good."
    arl "Bien."

# game/episode014.rpy:538
translate spanish uailea_council_55071d32:

#   arl "Several months ago, my esteemed colleague Nkoy Rhedia vanished without a trace."
    arl "Hace varios meses, mi estimado colega Nkoy Rhedia desapareció sin dejar rastro."

# game/episode014.rpy:539
translate spanish uailea_council_d8a07738:

#   arl "Nkoy Rhedia has been a respected scholar for many years, but lately her behavior became erratic."
    arl "Nkoy Rhedia ha sido una respetada académica durante muchos años, pero últimamente su comportamiento se ha vuelto errático."

# game/episode014.rpy:541
translate spanish uailea_council_16a8b997:

#   zi "Nkoy Rhedia, erratic?"
    zi "Nkoy Rhedia, ¿errático?"

# game/episode014.rpy:542
translate spanish uailea_council_df705584:

#   c "You know her, Ziv?"
    c "¿La conoces, Ziv?"

# game/episode014.rpy:543
translate spanish uailea_council_7ab6b011:

#   zi "Everybody knows of Nkoy Rhedia, she's very influential."
    zi "Todo el mundo conoce a Nkoy Rhedia, es muy influyente."

# game/episode014.rpy:545
translate spanish uailea_council_65ad4d00:

#   arl "Indeed she is, and it makes her apparent downfall all the more regretful."
    arl "Así es, y eso hace que su aparente caída sea aún más lamentable."

# game/episode014.rpy:546
translate spanish uailea_council_ffb1131f:

#   arl "The more recent writings of Nkoy Rhedia began to challenge the order of the Rhenkoy here on Uailea more and more."
    arl "Los escritos más recientes de Nkoy Rhedia empezaron a cuestionar cada vez más el orden de los Rhenkoy aquí en Uailea."

# game/episode014.rpy:547
translate spanish uailea_council_57476a59:

#   arl "Of course, she has always been a very sharp and critical thinker, but her last outpourings were on the verge of sedition."
    arl "Por supuesto, siempre ha sido una pensadora muy aguda y crítica, pero sus últimos desahogos estaban al borde de la sedición."

# game/episode014.rpy:549
translate spanish uailea_council_b7e49054:

#   zi "Sedition?"
    zi "¿Sedición?"

# game/episode014.rpy:551
translate spanish uailea_council_61c62157:

#   arl "She started to challenge the very fabric of our society."
    arl "Empezó a cuestionar el tejido mismo de nuestra sociedad."

# game/episode014.rpy:552
translate spanish uailea_council_48197095:

#   c "Surely she's free to be critical of the world she lives in?"
    c "Seguro que es libre de ser crítica con el mundo en el que vive."

# game/episode014.rpy:553
translate spanish uailea_council_6cdb2f39:

#   arl "Of course she is, so the Council didn't intervene."
    arl "Claro que sí, por eso el Consejo no intervino."

# game/episode014.rpy:554
translate spanish uailea_council_ed086411:

#   arl "Only when she started living in seclusion with her most ardent students, we began to worry."
    arl "Sólo cuando empezó a vivir recluida con sus alumnos más acérrimos, empezamos a preocuparnos."

# game/episode014.rpy:555
translate spanish uailea_council_dab698e2:

#   c "How come?"
    c "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode014.rpy:557
translate spanish uailea_council_c5adcf3d:

#   arl "The tone of her writings took on a decidedly militant note."
    arl "El tono de sus escritos adquirió un tono decididamente militante."

# game/episode014.rpy:558
translate spanish uailea_council_0ae63e6d:

#   arl "Her students also spread out all across Uailea to tell tales about the supposed corruption at the root of Rhenkoy society and recruit new members for the cause."
    arl "Sus alumnos también se esparcieron por todo Uailea para contar historias sobre la supuesta corrupción en la raíz de la sociedad Rhenkoy y reclutar nuevos miembros para la causa."

# game/episode014.rpy:559
translate spanish uailea_council_29c5ea35:

#   arl "A delegation attempted to visit Nkoy Rhedia in her compound to discuss her grievances."
    arl "Una delegación intentó visitar a Nkoy Rhedia en su recinto para discutir sus quejas."

# game/episode014.rpy:560
translate spanish uailea_council_d4332053:

#   arl "They found the compound empty and booby-trapped."
    arl "Encontraron el complejo vacío y con trampas explosivas."

# game/episode014.rpy:562
translate spanish uailea_council_6f497cec:

#   arl "Several members of the delegation lost their lives."
    arl "Varios miembros de la delegación perdieron la vida."

# game/episode014.rpy:564
translate spanish uailea_council_3b9452ec:

#   arl "We believe the Nkoy is hiding in the wilderness of Uailea, together with her followers."
    arl "Creemos que la Nkoy se esconde en el desierto de Uailea, junto con sus seguidores."

# game/episode014.rpy:565
translate spanish uailea_council_daadbf77:

#   arl "Her disciples are seldom seen in public, and it's been several weeks since her last missive."
    arl "Rara vez se ve a sus discípulos en público, y han pasado varias semanas desde su última misiva."

# game/episode014.rpy:566
translate spanish uailea_council_af76917a:

#   arl "We do however think Nkoy Rhedia has not given up her fight against the so-called corruption."
    arl "No obstante, creemos que Nkoy Rhedia no ha renunciado a su lucha contra la llamada corrupción."

# game/episode014.rpy:567
translate spanish uailea_council_687f4625:

#   arl "Instead, we think she's preparing to strike violently against the heart of Rhenkoy democracy from her base in the wilderness."
    arl "En cambio, creemos que se está preparando para golpear violentamente el corazón de la democracia Rhenkoy desde su base en el desierto."

# game/episode014.rpy:569
translate spanish uailea_council_4a333844:

#   zi "I can't believe Nkoy Rhedia would resort to violence."
    zi "No puedo creer que Nkoy Rhedia recurra a la violencia."

# game/episode014.rpy:571
translate spanish uailea_council_21ccfe49:

#   arl "The Council couldn't either, until the gruesome attack on the delegation."
    arl "El Consejo tampoco podía, hasta el espantoso ataque a la delegación."

# game/episode014.rpy:583
translate spanish uailea_council_4bcb2997:

#   c "What would you have us do?"
    c "¿Qué quiere que hagamos?"

# game/episode014.rpy:585
translate spanish uailea_council_34d7b86b:

#   arl "Sending out armed forces on an official mission to root out the rebels is out of the question."
    arl "El envío de fuerzas armadas en misión oficial para erradicar a los rebeldes está descartado."

# game/episode014.rpy:586
translate spanish uailea_council_be8b7287:

#   c "How so?"
    c "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode014.rpy:588
translate spanish uailea_council_e50ca7be:

#   arl "We don't want the Nkoy harmed."
    arl "No queremos que los Nkoy sufran daños."

# game/episode014.rpy:589
translate spanish uailea_council_010003de:

#   arl "Nor her students, if it can be helped."
    arl "Ni a sus alumnos, si puede evitarse."

# game/episode014.rpy:591
translate spanish uailea_council_92b60cbb:

#   arl "Besides, it would enflame what little support for Nkoy Rhedia's cause exists among the populace."
    arl "Además, avivaría el escaso apoyo a la causa de Nkoy Rhedia que existe entre la población."

# game/episode014.rpy:592
translate spanish uailea_council_58e909cf:

#   arl "We would ask you to go into the wilderness and find Nkoy Rhedia."
    arl "Te pedimos que vayas al desierto y encuentres a Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode014.rpy:593
translate spanish uailea_council_befe92ed:

#   arl "And once you've found the Nkoy, we would ask you to reason with her and convince her to come back to society and argue her case before the Council."
    arl "Y una vez que hayas encontrado a la Nkoy, te pediríamos que razonaras con ella y la convencieras para que vuelva a la sociedad y exponga su caso ante el Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:594
translate spanish uailea_council_87178749:

#   c "And if she doesn't agree to come with us?"
    c "¿Y si no acepta venir con nosotros?"

# game/episode014.rpy:596
translate spanish uailea_council_158a98ea:

#   arl "We'd leave any decision in your hands, however regrettable it may turn out to be."
    arl "Dejaríamos en sus manos cualquier decisión, por lamentable que resulte."

# game/episode014.rpy:597
translate spanish uailea_council_964b1d7a:

#   arl "I must stress the need for discreetness, the political situation is too volatile."
    arl "Debo insistir en la necesidad de discreción, la situación política es demasiado volátil."

# game/episode014.rpy:599
translate spanish uailea_council_fe0b6a67:

#   zi "I had no idea."
    zi "No tenía ni idea."

# game/episode014.rpy:601
translate spanish uailea_council_77f22e77:

#   arl "Much has changed since your departure."
    arl "Mucho ha cambiado desde su partida."

# game/episode014.rpy:602
translate spanish uailea_council_c39b08da:

#   c "If we agree to capture this Nkoy Rhedia, the Council will allow us to see the Scolguin?"
    c "Si aceptamos capturar a este Nkoy Rhedia, ¿el Consejo nos permitirá ver al Scolguin?"

# game/episode014.rpy:604
translate spanish uailea_council_f306214f:

#   arl "You have my word."
    arl "Te doy mi palabra."

# game/episode014.rpy:605
translate spanish uailea_council_085246ff:

#   arl "I will be your liaison to the Council."
    arl "Seré su enlace con el Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:606
translate spanish uailea_council_f8cdb4d1:

#   arl "You will deliver Nkoy Rhedia into my custody if she agrees to travel back with you, and I will make the arrangements for you to meet with the Scolguin."
    arl "Entregarás a Nkoy Rhedia bajo mi custodia si acepta viajar de vuelta contigo, y yo haré los arreglos para que te reúnas con el Scolguin."

# game/episode014.rpy:608
translate spanish uailea_council_510990c3:

#   arl "Of course, if anything goes awry, the Council and myself will deny any involvement."
    arl "Por supuesto, si algo sale mal, el Consejo y yo mismo negaremos cualquier implicación."

# game/episode014.rpy:609
translate spanish uailea_council_772f3df2:

#   arl "I trust you understand the need for deniability?"
    arl "Confío en que entiendas la necesidad de la negación."

# game/episode014.rpy:610
translate spanish uailea_council_d7269434:

#   c "I think I do."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:612
translate spanish uailea_council_ec0b88b9:

#   arl "Do we have a deal?"
    arl "¿Tenemos un trato?"

# game/episode014.rpy:613
translate spanish uailea_council_708400eb:

#   c "Yes, we do."
    c "Pues sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:615
translate spanish uailea_council_e2053404:

#   arl "Excellent."
    arl "Excelente."

# game/episode014.rpy:616
translate spanish uailea_council_a23d97de:

#   arl "I'll be sure to forward you the possible location of Nkoy Rhedia."
    arl "Me aseguraré de enviarle la posible ubicación de Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode014.rpy:618
translate spanish uailea_council_ea5ec9cb:

#   arl "Beware that this information is approximate and based on sketchy intelligence."
    arl "Tenga en cuenta que esta información es aproximada y se basa en datos poco fiables."

# game/episode014.rpy:619
translate spanish uailea_council_7963cf59:

#   c "Understood."
    c "Entendido."

# game/episode014.rpy:620
translate spanish uailea_council_f901276b:

#   arl "You may contact me again once you're ready to turn Nkoy Rhedia over to my custody."
    arl "Puede volver a ponerse en contacto conmigo cuando esté listo para entregar a Nkoy Rhedia a mi custodia."

# game/episode014.rpy:622
translate spanish uailea_council_4e645f8f:

#   arl "Good luck, captain."
    arl "Buena suerte, capitán."

# game/episode014.rpy:624
translate spanish uailea_council_f76b8dbc:

#   "With those words, Arlya left the room."
    "Con estas palabras, Arlya abandonó la habitación."

# game/episode014.rpy:639
translate spanish uailea_council_6a54c044:

#   c "Quite the tale, don't you think?"
    c "Toda una historia, ¿no crees?"

# game/episode014.rpy:640
translate spanish uailea_council_4d998aa0:

#   zi "Yes, quite..."
    zi "Sí, bastante..."

# game/episode014.rpy:641
translate spanish uailea_council_66cb9f92:

#   c "What do you think about all that she told us?"
    c "¿Qué te parece todo lo que nos ha contado?"

# game/episode014.rpy:644
translate spanish uailea_council_967c8108:

#   zi "As she said, Nkoy Rhedia has a very sharp tongue, but her resorting to violence seems like a stretch."
    zi "Como ella misma ha dicho, Nkoy Rhedia tiene una lengua muy afilada, pero que recurra a la violencia parece una exageración."

# game/episode014.rpy:646
translate spanish uailea_council_de0be94f:

#   zi "Then again, there doesn't seem to be any other way to access those Scolguin prisoners."
    zi "Por otra parte, no parece haber otra forma de acceder a esos prisioneros escolguines."

# game/episode014.rpy:647
translate spanish uailea_council_f8165dbe:

#   c "No, I think we need to go ahead with the task."
    c "No, creo que debemos seguir adelante con la tarea."

# game/episode014.rpy:648
translate spanish uailea_council_5ba039f2:

#   c "Could you ask around about what happened with Rhedia, though?"
    c "Pero, ¿podrías preguntar por ahí qué pasó con Rhedia?"

# game/episode014.rpy:649
translate spanish uailea_council_eba9ddb1:

#   c "I'm sure Arlya told us as much as we needed to know, but it might be good to get another perspective on the matter."
    c "Estoy seguro de que Arlya nos ha contado todo lo que necesitábamos saber, pero sería bueno tener otra perspectiva del asunto."

# game/episode014.rpy:651
translate spanish uailea_council_b129986d:

#   zi "Of course, that sounds like a good idea."
    zi "Por supuesto, parece una buena idea."

# game/episode014.rpy:652
translate spanish uailea_council_17690a93:

#   c "I'll head back to the ship and inform the others about our latest adventure."
    c "Volveré a la nave e informaré a los demás de nuestra última aventura."

# game/episode014.rpy:653
translate spanish uailea_council_430582c7:

#   zi "Good, I'll meet you back on the ship."
    zi "Bien, nos vemos en la nave."

# game/episode014.rpy:656
translate spanish uailea_council_1ac796cb:

#   "After I brought everyone up to speed, Céline and I found a landing spot near the coordinates Arlya had sent us."
    "Después de poner a todo el mundo al corriente, Céline y yo encontramos un punto de aterrizaje cerca de las coordenadas que Arlya nos había enviado."

# game/episode014.rpy:657
translate spanish uailea_council_d2c14cf3:

#   "As Ziv hadn’t returned yet, we all had some time to kill."
    "Como Ziv aún no había vuelto, todos teníamos tiempo que perder."

# game/episode014.rpy:643
translate spanish uailea_council_87322771_1:

#   zi "I'm not sure."
    zi "No estoy seguro."

# game/episode014.rpy:662
translate spanish uailea_tand_4781effe:

#   "Ziv arrived after a few hours and visited me in my quarters."
    "Ziv llegó al cabo de unas horas y me visitó en mis aposentos."

# game/episode014.rpy:663
translate spanish uailea_tand_98e9e024:

#   c "Arlya has sent us the necessary information, so we're ready to go."
    c "Arlya nos ha enviado la información necesaria, así que estamos listos para partir."

# game/episode014.rpy:664
translate spanish uailea_tand_e2134650:

#   c "Have you found out anything useful?"
    c "¿Ha descubierto algo útil?"

# game/episode014.rpy:666
translate spanish uailea_tand_31d4e678:

#   zi "Not much."
    zi "No mucho."

# game/episode014.rpy:667
translate spanish uailea_tand_ba3f09b8:

#   zi "Nkoy Rhedia seems to have accused the Council of corruption and demanded a public inquest."
    zi "Al parecer, Nkoy Rhedia acusó al Consejo de corrupción y exigió una investigación pública."

# game/episode014.rpy:668
translate spanish uailea_tand_ee886b88:

#   zi "After it became clear there was to be no investigation, she began to advocate for violence as she grew more and more isolated."
    zi "Cuando quedó claro que no iba a haber investigación, empezó a abogar por la violencia a medida que se iba quedando cada vez más aislada."

# game/episode014.rpy:669
translate spanish uailea_tand_962ed5a7:

#   zi "I was also able to verify some of what Nkoy Arlya told us about the incident at the compound."
    zi "También pude verificar parte de lo que Nkoy Arlya nos contó sobre el incidente en el recinto."

# game/episode014.rpy:670
translate spanish uailea_tand_03bd29a0:

#   zi "A delegation seems to have visited the place, after which explosions and possibly gunfire was heard."
    zi "Al parecer, una delegación visitó el lugar, tras lo cual se oyeron explosiones y posiblemente disparos."

# game/episode014.rpy:672
translate spanish uailea_tand_ef3794ee:

#   zi "Nothing else has been made public about the incident, but all stories confirm the departure of Nkoy Rhedia to an unknown location far into the wildlands of Uailea."
    zi "No se ha hecho público nada más sobre el incidente, pero todas las historias confirman la marcha de Nkoy Rhedia a un lugar desconocido, lejos en las tierras salvajes de Uailea."

# game/episode014.rpy:673
translate spanish uailea_tand_caabe90f:

#   c "Let's find Rhedia then and learn more."
    c "Busquemos entonces a Rhedia y sepamos más."

# game/episode014.rpy:674
translate spanish uailea_tand_5f09ea17:

#   c "We're going to touch down near Tand."
    c "Vamos a aterrizar cerca de Tand."

# game/episode014.rpy:675
translate spanish uailea_tand_5776a45d:

#   zi "That sounds good."
    zi "Eso suena bien."

# game/episode014.rpy:678
translate spanish uailea_tand_067961cc:

#   zi "I believe Tand is a place very similar to the one I grew up in."
    zi "Creo que Tand es un lugar muy parecido a aquel en el que crecí."

# game/episode014.rpy:679
translate spanish uailea_tand_5c4cac00:

#   zi "The wilderness of Uailea is quite beautiful, I just wish you'd see it under different circumstances."
    zi "La naturaleza salvaje de Uailea es muy hermosa, sólo desearía que la vieras en otras circunstancias."

# game/episode014.rpy:680
translate spanish uailea_tand_a76c4ea4:

#   c "I know, but it can't be helped, unfortunately."
    c "Lo sé, pero no se puede evitar, por desgracia."

# game/episode014.rpy:683
translate spanish uailea_tand_137fef76:

#   "Not long after Ziv had left my quarters, the ship took off in the direction of Tand."
    "Poco después de que Ziv abandonara mis aposentos, la nave despegó en dirección a Tand."

# game/episode014.rpy:685
translate spanish uailea_tand_a8cca149:

#   "We touched down near the small village after a one-hour suborbital flight."
    "Aterrizamos cerca del pequeño pueblo tras una hora de vuelo suborbital."

# game/episode014.rpy:687
translate spanish uailea_tand_3da32a5b:

#   "Ziv, Aven, Kit and Jade were suited up and ready to accompany me after Céline had completed the landing sequence."
    "Ziv, Aven, Kit y Jade se habían vestido y estaban listos para acompañarme después de que Céline completara la secuencia de aterrizaje."

# game/episode014.rpy:688
translate spanish uailea_tand_4ba70d0c:

#   "The plan was to head out to Tand first and question the locals before heading out into the wilderness."
    "El plan era dirigirse primero a Tand e interrogar a los lugareños antes de adentrarse en el desierto."

# game/episode014.rpy:690
translate spanish uailea_tand_89223f1b:

#   "Tand turned out to be a quiet village, consisting of a few houses, some stores and public buildings."
    "Tand resultó ser un pueblo tranquilo, formado por unas pocas casas, algunas tiendas y edificios públicos."

# game/episode014.rpy:691
translate spanish uailea_tand_d58965fd:

#   "The architectural style favored by the Rhenkoy was very much in evidence here as well."
    "El estilo arquitectónico de los Rhenkoy también estaba muy presente aquí."

# game/episode014.rpy:703
translate spanish uailea_tand_09d77aec:

#   "Ziv had split from us before entering the town and would make her inquiries on her own."
    "Ziv se había separado de nosotros antes de entrar en la ciudad y haría sus averiguaciones por su cuenta."

# game/episode014.rpy:704
translate spanish uailea_tand_52b12c5a:

#   "We in turn posed as tourists to provide backup if necessary."
    "Nosotros, por nuestra parte, nos hicimos pasar por turistas para prestar apoyo en caso necesario."

# game/episode014.rpy:705
translate spanish uailea_tand_a0d3d297:

#   "I'm aware our cover story was rather flimsy, but Ziv assured me some form of tourism existed on Uailea."
    "Soy consciente de que nuestra tapadera era bastante endeble, pero Ziv me aseguró que existía algún tipo de turismo en Uailea."

# game/episode014.rpy:707
translate spanish uailea_tand_42112350:

#   "At any rate, the locals didn't seem bothered by the aliens roaming in their village."
    "En cualquier caso, a los lugareños no parecía molestarles que los alienígenas vagaran por su pueblo."

# game/episode014.rpy:709
translate spanish uailea_tand_f791e971:

#   "The Rhenkoy we met weren't very talkative though, until we met the owner of the general store of Tand."
    "Sin embargo, los Rhenkoy que conocimos no eran muy habladores, hasta que conocimos al dueño del almacén general de Tand."

# game/episode014.rpy:712
translate spanish uailea_tand_c89a1d3b:

#   woman "Welcome, feel free to browse as long as you want!"
    woman "Bienvenido, ¡no dude en navegar todo el tiempo que quiera!"

# game/episode014.rpy:713
translate spanish uailea_tand_76403196:

#   "The woman seemed positively thrilled to meet us."
    "La mujer parecía encantada de conocernos."

# game/episode014.rpy:714
translate spanish uailea_tand_096c5a6e:

#   c "Thank you for the enthusiastic welcome."
    c "Gracias por la entusiasta bienvenida."

# game/episode014.rpy:715
translate spanish uailea_tand_514fcd5d:

#   woman "We don't get many visitors around here."
    woman "No recibimos muchas visitas por aquí."

# game/episode014.rpy:717
translate spanish uailea_tand_043d4f27:

#   woman "Are you a hunting party?"
    woman "¿Sois una partida de caza?"

# game/episode014.rpy:718
translate spanish uailea_tand_053ee927:

#   c "Something like that, yes."
    c "Algo así, sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:720
translate spanish uailea_tand_fcaa2323:

#   woman "Judging from the arms you and your friends carry, you came prepared."
    woman "A juzgar por las armas que lleváis tú y tus amigos, habéis venido preparados."

# game/episode014.rpy:721
translate spanish uailea_tand_bce2dfde:

#   woman "The woods are full of wildlife, so you'll be sure to find some sport there."
    woman "Los bosques están llenos de vida salvaje, así que seguro que encuentras algún deporte allí."

# game/episode014.rpy:722
translate spanish uailea_tand_c710afa7:

#   "The store owner was obviously eager to talk, so I let her ramble on."
    "La dueña de la tienda tenía muchas ganas de hablar, así que la dejé que siguiera divagando."

# game/episode014.rpy:723
translate spanish uailea_tand_cd929723:

#   woman "Just be careful out there, though."
    woman "Pero ten cuidado ahí fuera."

# game/episode014.rpy:724
translate spanish uailea_tand_bfa1b18d:

#   c "How come, are any of the animals dangerous?"
    c "¿Cómo es posible que alguno de los animales sea peligroso?"

# game/episode014.rpy:726
translate spanish uailea_tand_da8f474b:

#   woman "No, not at all."
    woman "No, en absoluto."

# game/episode014.rpy:728
translate spanish uailea_tand_e8965686:

#   woman "But recently, a small group of people have been living in the woods."
    woman "Pero desde hace poco, un pequeño grupo de personas vive en el bosque."

# game/episode014.rpy:729
translate spanish uailea_tand_937ae57e:

#   woman "You wouldn't want to mistake anyone for target practice."
    woman "No querrías confundir a nadie con una práctica de tiro."

# game/episode014.rpy:730
translate spanish uailea_tand_e9a485d8:

#   c "Very good to know."
    c "Es bueno saberlo."

# game/episode014.rpy:731
translate spanish uailea_tand_904b0e9c:

#   c "Do you know where those people have made their home, just so we can avoid them?"
    c "¿Sabes dónde se han instalado esas personas para que podamos evitarlas?"

# game/episode014.rpy:733
translate spanish uailea_tand_4790cc35:

#   woman "I'm afraid not, they do come in here to get supplies from time to time."
    woman "Me temo que no, vienen aquí a abastecerse de vez en cuando."

# game/episode014.rpy:734
translate spanish uailea_tand_68a70784:

#   woman "They're friendly, but they do keep to themselves."
    woman "Son amistosos, pero muy reservados."

# game/episode014.rpy:736
translate spanish uailea_tand_19f6dc5d:

#   c "We'll be sure not to disturb their home once we head out into the wilderness."
    c "Nos aseguraremos de no perturbar su hogar cuando nos adentremos en la naturaleza."

# game/episode014.rpy:737
translate spanish uailea_tand_cd523a6a:

#   "Some other customers had entered the store at that point, so I said goodbye to the owner and went back out on the street with the others."
    "Otros clientes habían entrado en la tienda en ese momento, así que me despedí del dueño y volví a la calle con los demás."

# game/episode014.rpy:739
translate spanish uailea_tand_8a6e4154:

#   "Ziv met up with us at the edge of the town at the agreed upon time."
    "Ziv se reunió con nosotros en las afueras de la ciudad a la hora acordada."

# game/episode014.rpy:740
translate spanish uailea_tand_22d5d0b3:

#   c "According to the owner of the general store, Rhedia's disciples regularly buy supplies in Tand."
    c "Según el propietario del almacén general, los discípulos de Rhedia compran regularmente provisiones en Tand."

# game/episode014.rpy:741
translate spanish uailea_tand_b09e27df:

#   c "She couldn't tell us where they came from, though."
    c "Sin embargo, no pudo decirnos de dónde venían."

# game/episode014.rpy:743
translate spanish uailea_tand_b52df9f8:

#   zi "I've heard the same."
    zi "He oído lo mismo."

# game/episode014.rpy:744
translate spanish uailea_tand_01a1d497:

#   zi "Apparently, they enter Tand from the east side of the village."
    zi "Al parecer, entran en Tand por el lado este del pueblo."

# game/episode014.rpy:746
translate spanish uailea_tand_8e597c48:

#   av "We might head out into the wilderness from that direction then."
    av "Podríamos adentrarnos en el desierto desde esa dirección entonces."

# game/episode014.rpy:747
translate spanish uailea_tand_1d02ddec:

#   c "Did you learn anything else?"
    c "¿Has aprendido algo más?"

# game/episode014.rpy:749
translate spanish uailea_tand_fbce392b:

#   zi "Nothing much."
    zi "No mucho."

# game/episode014.rpy:750
translate spanish uailea_tand_a0d7ece0:

#   zi "Nobody has approached them in the wilderness, it seems."
    zi "Parece que nadie se ha acercado a ellos en el desierto."

# game/episode014.rpy:751
translate spanish uailea_tand_7a9bf8da:

#   zi "They just live there in solitude."
    zi "Sólo viven allí en soledad."

# game/episode014.rpy:752
translate spanish uailea_tand_c09f1291:

#   c "Do the locals regard them as dangerous?"
    c "¿Los lugareños los consideran peligrosos?"

# game/episode014.rpy:753
translate spanish uailea_tand_677156b8:

#   zi "No, I haven't heard anything about that."
    zi "No, no he oído nada al respecto."

# game/episode014.rpy:754
translate spanish uailea_tand_59da6ab0:

#   zi "Though the villagers of Tand have left Nkoy Rhedia and her followers in peace since their arrival."
    zi "Aunque los aldeanos de Tand han dejado en paz a Nkoy Rhedia y sus seguidores desde su llegada."

# game/episode014.rpy:755
translate spanish uailea_tand_826a1fde:

#   c "Let's not take any chances and be prepared for anything out there."
    c "No nos arriesguemos y estemos preparados para cualquier cosa."

# game/episode014.rpy:757
translate spanish uailea_tand_abe36ad9:

#   ki "Understood."
    ki "Entendido."

# game/episode014.rpy:759
translate spanish uailea_tand_15c9208d:

#   "We made our way to the outskirts of the village in the general direction Ziv had indicated."
    "Nos dirigimos a las afueras del pueblo en la dirección general que nos había indicado Ziv."

# game/episode014.rpy:761
translate spanish uailea_tand_7255b7ef:

#   c "Before we go into the wilderness, I'd like to discuss tactics."
    c "Antes de adentrarnos en el desierto, me gustaría hablar de tácticas."

# game/episode014.rpy:765
translate spanish uailea_tand_1dbd3512:

#   c "The followers of Nkoy Rhedia are likely to be very dangerous."
    c "Los seguidores de Nkoy Rhedia pueden ser muy peligrosos."

# game/episode014.rpy:766
translate spanish uailea_tand_783b953c:

#   c "I don't want us to end up like the last team who tried to contact her and got blown to bits."
    c "No quiero que acabemos como el último equipo que intentó contactar con ella y voló en pedazos."

# game/episode014.rpy:767
translate spanish uailea_tand_777b786c:

#   c "If anyone points a gun at you, don't hesitate to pull the trigger."
    c "Si alguien te apunta con un arma, no dudes en apretar el gatillo."

# game/episode014.rpy:769
translate spanish uailea_tand_1c6189b1:

#   zi "Are you sure we need to be that aggressive?"
    zi "¿Estás seguro de que tenemos que ser tan agresivos?"

# game/episode014.rpy:770
translate spanish uailea_tand_7ec9bf22:

#   c "I don't want to take any chances."
    c "No quiero correr riesgos."

# game/episode014.rpy:771
translate spanish uailea_tand_38589aa8:

#   c "I know Rhedia is supposed to be a respected figure, but her recent actions speak very much to the contrary."
    c "Sé que se supone que Rhedia es una figura respetada, pero sus recientes acciones dicen mucho de lo contrario."

# game/episode014.rpy:773
translate spanish uailea_tand_4200c74d:

#   c "I know there have been some stories floating around about Nkoy Rhedia's violent streak."
    c "Sé que han circulado algunas historias sobre la vena violenta de Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode014.rpy:774
translate spanish uailea_tand_82b76b95:

#   c "I want us to be very careful and don't go in guns blazing."
    c "Quiero que seamos muy cuidadosos y que no entremos disparando."

# game/episode014.rpy:775
translate spanish uailea_tand_70c47a57:

#   c "Rhedia likely has a superior force and knows these woods in ways we don't."
    c "Es probable que Rhedia tenga una fuerza superior y conozca estos bosques como nosotros no."

# game/episode014.rpy:776
translate spanish uailea_tand_9da8d7cf:

#   c "We don't shoot to kill unless threatened in the same way ourselves."
    c "No disparamos a matar a menos que nosotros mismos nos veamos amenazados de la misma manera."

# game/episode014.rpy:777
translate spanish uailea_tand_e5e59c44:

#   c "This doesn't have to become a blood bath."
    c "Esto no tiene por qué convertirse en un baño de sangre."

# game/episode014.rpy:779
translate spanish uailea_tand_eb0c28ba:

#   zi "Understood."
    zi "Entendido."

# game/episode014.rpy:784
translate spanish uailea_tand_1c6d201e:

#   "Guns at the ready, we headed out into what's best described as a forest."
    "Con las armas preparadas, nos adentramos en lo que podría describirse como un bosque."

# game/episode014.rpy:785
translate spanish uailea_tand_4e8178aa:

#   "We didn't see any signs of life, except for the local wildlife skittering away as soon as we encountered them."
    "No vimos señales de vida, salvo la fauna local, que se alejó en cuanto la vimos."

# game/episode014.rpy:787
translate spanish uailea_tand_959b56f4:

#   "After three hours, I began to think this whole expedition was doomed from the start."
    "Después de tres horas, empecé a pensar que toda esta expedición estaba condenada desde el principio."

# game/episode014.rpy:788
translate spanish uailea_tand_daf27b0b:

#   "At that moment, Aven motioned us to stop."
    "En ese momento, Aven nos indicó que nos detuviéramos."

# game/episode014.rpy:790
translate spanish uailea_tand_8331d66a:

#   av "Tracks in the underbrush, recent."
    av "Huellas en la maleza, recientes."

# game/episode014.rpy:791
translate spanish uailea_tand_384f335c:

#   c "Humanoid?"
    c "¿Humanoide?"

# game/episode014.rpy:792
translate spanish uailea_tand_e329f1ff:

#   av "Unless the large game here started wearing boots, I'd wager humanoid."
    av "A menos que el gran juego aquí comenzó a usar botas, yo apostaría humanoide."

# game/episode014.rpy:793
translate spanish uailea_tand_7164c981:

#   c "Okay, spread out and follow those tracks."
    c "Bien, dispérsense y sigan esas huellas."

# game/episode014.rpy:795
translate spanish uailea_tand_8af51362:

#   "Aven and Kit took the lead following the tracks into the forest."
    "Aven y Kit tomaron la delantera siguiendo las huellas hacia el bosque."

# game/episode014.rpy:796
translate spanish uailea_tand_a1601795:

#   "There was no clear path that we could see, but this route seemed to have been used regularly."
    "No había un camino claro que pudiéramos ver, pero esta ruta parecía haber sido utilizada con regularidad."

# game/episode014.rpy:797
translate spanish uailea_tand_9fcb5c61:

#   "Careful not to expose ourselves to hidden gunmen, we continued our trek."
    "Con cuidado de no exponernos a pistoleros ocultos, continuamos nuestra marcha."

# game/episode014.rpy:799
translate spanish uailea_tand_b940f9f3:

#   "After a few miles, Aven made us stop again and produced a set of binoculars."
    "Al cabo de unos kilómetros, Aven nos hizo parar de nuevo y sacó unos prismáticos."

# game/episode014.rpy:800
translate spanish uailea_tand_dbcc41c8:

#   av "Sentries up ahead."
    av "Centinelas adelante."

# game/episode014.rpy:801
translate spanish uailea_tand_3498231e:

#   "Aven passed me the binoculars."
    "Aven me pasó los prismáticos."

# game/episode014.rpy:802
translate spanish uailea_tand_236704f8:

#   c "You're right, how did you know?"
    c "Tienes razón, ¿cómo lo sabías?"

# game/episode014.rpy:804
translate spanish uailea_tand_d7d8340b:

#   av "I thought I saw something move up there."
    av "Me pareció ver que algo se movía allá arriba."

# game/episode014.rpy:805
translate spanish uailea_tand_a83f22ee:

#   c "They're not extremely well-hidden."
    c "No están muy bien escondidos."

# game/episode014.rpy:806
translate spanish uailea_tand_fd44c21a:

#   av "No, they're not."
    av "No, no lo son."

# game/episode014.rpy:807
translate spanish uailea_tand_eba73ef1:

#   c "Can you tell how many of them there are?"
    c "¿Sabe cuántos hay?"

# game/episode014.rpy:808
translate spanish uailea_tand_6be90791:

#   av "Three on this side, six, maybe eight in total."
    av "Tres en este lado, seis, tal vez ocho en total."

# game/episode014.rpy:810
translate spanish uailea_tand_34f36db6:

#   av "How do we proceed?"
    av "¿Cómo proceder?"

# game/episode014.rpy:812
translate spanish uailea_tand_7ece25bb:

#   c "We fan out and take them out from behind."
    c "Nos desplegamos y los derribamos por detrás."

# game/episode014.rpy:814
translate spanish uailea_tand_53e50f32:

#   c "We fan out and hold them at gunpoint, maybe we can reason with them."
    c "Nos desplegamos y los retenemos a punta de pistola, tal vez podamos razonar con ellos."

# game/episode014.rpy:815
translate spanish uailea_tand_b5fa9b86:

#   av "Risky, but doable."
    av "Arriesgado, pero factible."

# game/episode014.rpy:817
translate spanish uailea_tand_ee272f69:

#   c "Spread out, fire on my mark."
    c "Dispérsense, fuego a mi señal."

# game/episode014.rpy:819
translate spanish uailea_tand_e8f0c6e7:

#   c "Spread out, don't fire unless I give the order."
    c "Dispérsense, no disparen a menos que yo dé la orden."

# game/episode014.rpy:821
translate spanish uailea_tand_a379acb8:

#   "It didn't take us long to surround the sentries."
    "No tardamos mucho en rodear a los centinelas."

# game/episode014.rpy:823
translate spanish uailea_tand_9f558a4e:

#   "My target was lounging against a tree, oblivious to her surroundings."
    "Mi objetivo estaba recostado contra un árbol, ajeno a su entorno."

# game/episode014.rpy:825
translate spanish uailea_tand_8c6b13aa:

#   "I quietly gave the signal to attack via radio and fired."
    "Tranquilamente di la señal de ataque por radio y disparé."

# game/episode014.rpy:827
translate spanish uailea_tand_3021b50f:

#   "Several gunshots resonated through the forest."
    "Varios disparos resonaron en el bosque."

# game/episode014.rpy:829
translate spanish uailea_tand_449f34ff:

#   c "Target eliminated."
    c "Objetivo eliminado."

# game/episode014.rpy:830
translate spanish uailea_tand_b47e5a18:

#   "Aven, Jade and Kit radioed me their kills."
    "Aven, Jade y Kit me comunicaron por radio sus muertes."

# game/episode014.rpy:831
translate spanish uailea_tand_82befb7a:

#   "Only Ziv's channel stayed silent."
    "Sólo el canal de Ziv permaneció en silencio."

# game/episode014.rpy:832
translate spanish uailea_tand_f11f22bc:

#   c "Ziv, do you copy?"
    c "Ziv, ¿me recibes?"

# game/episode014.rpy:833
translate spanish uailea_tand_4b29505e:

#   c "Ziv?!"
    c "¡¿Ziv?!"

# game/episode014.rpy:834
translate spanish uailea_tand_60058cd1:

#   zi "Yes, I'm here."
    zi "Sí, aquí estoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:835
translate spanish uailea_tand_ca920b12:

#   c "Have you eliminated your target."
    c "¿Ha eliminado su objetivo."

# game/episode014.rpy:836
translate spanish uailea_tand_ed36e26c:

#   zi "No, she got away."
    zi "No, se escapó."

# game/episode014.rpy:837
translate spanish uailea_tand_0f3ca2e2:

#   c "Dammit!"
    c "¡Maldita sea!"

# game/episode014.rpy:838
translate spanish uailea_tand_56cdd477:

#   c "Regroup at my position."
    c "Reagruparos en mi posición."

# game/episode014.rpy:840
translate spanish uailea_tand_282ec226:

#   "One by one, my crew circled back towards my location."
    "Uno a uno, mi tripulación volvió en círculos hacia mi ubicación."

# game/episode014.rpy:841
translate spanish uailea_tand_b2cdb213:

#   c "What happened back there, Ziv?"
    c "¿Qué pasó allí, Ziv?"

# game/episode014.rpy:843
translate spanish uailea_tand_be5709db:

#   zi "I just...{w} I couldn't do it."
    zi "Yo sólo...{w} No pude hacerlo."

# game/episode014.rpy:844
translate spanish uailea_tand_1c0f508b:

#   c "They could have shot you."
    c "Podrían haberte disparado."

# game/episode014.rpy:846
translate spanish uailea_tand_ffddbf96:

#   zi "I think that's highly unlikely."
    zi "Creo que es muy poco probable."

# game/episode014.rpy:847
translate spanish uailea_tand_62bc1d1d:

#   c "Well, we can be certain she's running back to get reinforcements."
    c "Bueno, podemos estar seguros de que está corriendo a buscar refuerzos."

# game/episode014.rpy:848
translate spanish uailea_tand_a5a1061f:

#   c "This whole mission has become a whole lot more dangerous."
    c "Toda esta misión se ha vuelto mucho más peligrosa."

# game/episode014.rpy:849
translate spanish uailea_tand_2f8e6d51:

#   c "Let me make one thing clear, when we're in the field and I give an order, I expect it to be followed."
    c "Permítanme dejar una cosa clara: cuando estamos sobre el terreno y doy una orden, espero que se cumpla."

# game/episode014.rpy:850
translate spanish uailea_tand_41cf06c8:

#   c "If you have a problem, you tell me in advance, not just before you have to pull the trigger."
    c "Si tienes un problema, dímelo con antelación, no justo antes de tener que apretar el gatillo."

# game/episode014.rpy:851
translate spanish uailea_tand_c56b5e15:

#   c "You put your own life on the line, but also that of others, and I won't have that."
    c "Te juegas la vida, pero también la de los demás, y eso no lo permitiré."

# game/episode014.rpy:853
translate spanish uailea_tand_bb8ec118:

#   zi "I..."
    zi "I..."

# game/episode014.rpy:854
translate spanish uailea_tand_5fcc990b:

#   c "Is that understood?"
    c "¿Entendido?"

# game/episode014.rpy:856
translate spanish uailea_tand_1d6c56bc:

#   zi "Yes, [p_name]."
    zi "Sí, [p_name]."

# game/episode014.rpy:858
translate spanish uailea_tand_8ac01764:

#   c "Good, be prepared for anything."
    c "Bien, prepárate para cualquier cosa."

# game/episode014.rpy:859
translate spanish uailea_tand_a6986482:

#   c "We should assume the encampment is on high alert."
    c "Debemos asumir que el campamento está en alerta máxima."

# game/episode014.rpy:860
translate spanish uailea_tand_3e72d1bc:

#   c "So shoot if you can take the shot."
    c "Así que dispara si puedes disparar."

# game/episode014.rpy:861
translate spanish uailea_tand_fe494b85:

#   c "Does anybody have a problem with that?"
    c "¿Alguien tiene algún problema con eso?"

# game/episode014.rpy:863
translate spanish uailea_tand_61ba20ae:

#   "Even Ziv acquiesced, so we moved on towards our target."
    "Incluso Ziv accedió, así que avanzamos hacia nuestro objetivo."

# game/episode014.rpy:864
translate spanish uailea_tand_5fffc251:

#   "To our luck, we didn't encounter any more sentries and soon the bustle of the encampment could be heard in the distance."
    "Para nuestra suerte, no encontramos más centinelas y pronto se oyó a lo lejos el bullicio del campamento."

# game/episode014.rpy:865
translate spanish uailea_tand_422075a3:

#   "The camp dwellers made no effort to conceal their presence."
    "Los habitantes del campamento no hicieron ningún esfuerzo por ocultar su presencia."

# game/episode014.rpy:867
translate spanish uailea_tand_d70a8e8b:

#   "The escaped sentry had probably arrived and caused a panic."
    "El centinela fugado probablemente había llegado y causado el pánico."

# game/episode014.rpy:868
translate spanish uailea_tand_3cabbf89:

#   "While potentially dangerous, the chaos could also be an opportunity to overwhelm the enemy."
    "Aunque potencialmente peligroso, el caos también podría ser una oportunidad para abrumar al enemigo."

# game/episode014.rpy:869
translate spanish uailea_tand_b039fb46:

#   c "Guns at the ready, we're going to storm the camp."
    c "Armas en ristre, vamos a asaltar el campamento."

# game/episode014.rpy:871
translate spanish uailea_tand_bcb8dc1f:

#   ki "We should probably hit the center of the encampment, the more important people will be housed there."
    ki "Probablemente deberíamos ir al centro del campamento, la gente más importante se alojará allí."

# game/episode014.rpy:872
translate spanish uailea_tand_88df38a7:

#   c "Agreed."
    c "De acuerdo."

# game/episode014.rpy:874
translate spanish uailea_tand_a9d2155e:

#   c "On my mark."
    c "A mi señal."

# game/episode014.rpy:876
translate spanish uailea_tand_db6243d7:

#   "The crew broke into a run after I'd given the signal."
    "La tripulación echó a correr después de que yo diera la señal."

# game/episode014.rpy:877
translate spanish uailea_tand_61098c2d:

#   "The panic in the camp only heightened when several Rhenkoy noticed us emerging from the woods."
    "El pánico en el campamento aumentó cuando varios Rhenkoy nos vieron salir del bosque."

# game/episode014.rpy:879
translate spanish uailea_tand_ab2f0134:

#   "Some Rhenkoy struggled to get their weapons, but were gunned down before they could reach them."
    "Algunos Rhenkoy lucharon por conseguir sus armas, pero fueron abatidos antes de que pudieran alcanzarlas."

# game/episode014.rpy:880
translate spanish uailea_tand_ed3a9c96:

#   "The resistance against our onslaught, if it could be called that, was a downright mess."
    "La resistencia contra nuestra embestida, si es que puede llamarse así, fue un auténtico desastre."

# game/episode014.rpy:881
translate spanish uailea_tand_344571bb:

#   "Several Rhenkoy ran at the sight of their comrades being killed and we eventually reached the center of the camp without taking a single bullet."
    "Varios Rhenkoy corrieron al ver cómo mataban a sus camaradas y finalmente llegamos al centro del campamento sin recibir una sola bala."

# game/episode014.rpy:883
translate spanish uailea_tand_a9092b82:

#   c "Rhedia, you're surrounded!"
    c "Rhedia, ¡estás rodeada!"

# game/episode014.rpy:884
translate spanish uailea_tand_0ed51209:

#   c "Come out with your hands behind your head!"
    c "¡Sal con las manos detrás de la cabeza!"

# game/episode014.rpy:885
translate spanish uailea_tand_2fa6cefa:

#   "There was silence and for a moment I thought we'd hit the wrong settlement."
    "Se hizo el silencio y por un momento pensé que nos habíamos equivocado de asentamiento."

# game/episode014.rpy:890
translate spanish uailea_tand_b0fde67b:

#   "But then the door of the yurt slide open and Nkoy Rhedia emerged."
    "Pero entonces se abrió la puerta de la yurta y salió Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode014.rpy:897
translate spanish uailea_tand_2dfbae74:

#   c "On your knees."
    c "De rodillas."

# game/episode014.rpy:899
translate spanish uailea_tand_bbd6fccc:

#   "Looking at the carnage surrounding her, Rhedia sank to her knees."
    "Contemplando la carnicería que la rodeaba, Rhedia cayó de rodillas."

# game/episode014.rpy:901
translate spanish uailea_tand_24702347:

#   rh "What have you done?!"
    rh "¡¿Qué has hecho?!"

# game/episode014.rpy:903
translate spanish uailea_tand_c9ea60c4:

#   "Obviously these weren't seasoned guerrillas, let alone trained soldiers."
    "Obviamente no eran guerrilleros experimentados, y mucho menos soldados entrenados."

# game/episode014.rpy:904
translate spanish uailea_tand_d9840525:

#   "Just before I made a move, I radioed the others and gave the go ahead."
    "Justo antes de moverme, llamé por radio a los demás y les di el visto bueno."

# game/episode014.rpy:906
translate spanish uailea_tand_cdac0af3:

#   c "Drop your weapon!"
    c "¡Suelta el arma!"

# game/episode014.rpy:907
translate spanish uailea_tand_28456ea8:

#   "The woman nearly lost her balance against the tree."
    "La mujer estuvo a punto de perder el equilibrio contra el árbol."

# game/episode014.rpy:908
translate spanish uailea_tand_0db89a3e:

#   c "Hands up!"
    c "¡Manos arriba!"

# game/episode014.rpy:910
translate spanish uailea_tand_402ca7d0:

#   "Too flustered to even point her gun in the right direction, she let it fall to the ground and put her hands in the air."
    "Demasiado nerviosa para apuntar con su arma en la dirección correcta, la dejó caer al suelo y levantó las manos."

# game/episode014.rpy:911
translate spanish uailea_tand_8ff6912b:

#   "Aven, Jade, Kit and Ziv radioed their successes shortly after."
    "Aven, Jade, Kit y Ziv comunicaron por radio sus éxitos poco después."

# game/episode014.rpy:913
translate spanish uailea_tand_6534813e:

#   c "Alright, bring them to me."
    c "Muy bien, tráemelos."

# game/episode014.rpy:915
translate spanish uailea_tand_3661f786:

#   "While I busied myself tying up the Rhenkoy woman, the others arrived with their prisoners."
    "Mientras me ocupaba de atar a la mujer Rhenkoy, llegaron los demás con sus prisioneros."

# game/episode014.rpy:916
translate spanish uailea_tand_d0d4591a:

#   c "Nobody got away?"
    c "¿No se ha escapado nadie?"

# game/episode014.rpy:918
translate spanish uailea_tand_bf30a243:

#   ki "Nobody."
    ki "Nadie."

# game/episode014.rpy:920
translate spanish uailea_tand_6f9d3e71:

#   av "They were surprised to even encounter someone here."
    av "Se sorprendieron de encontrar a alguien aquí."

# game/episode014.rpy:921
translate spanish uailea_tand_0da143f5:

#   c "Not very smart, considering the Council is after them."
    c "No es muy inteligente, considerando que el Consejo está tras ellos."

# game/episode014.rpy:922
translate spanish uailea_tand_2bb5e5c3:

#   c "Are all of them cuffed?"
    c "¿Están todos esposados?"

# game/episode014.rpy:924
translate spanish uailea_tand_9f64a2bd:

#   j "Yes."
    j "Sí."

# game/episode014.rpy:925
translate spanish uailea_tand_f5f7c27d:

#   c "Right."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode014.rpy:926
translate spanish uailea_tand_f95355e7:

#   c "Listen up, don't try to escape or make sudden moves."
    c "Presta atención, no intentes escapar ni hagas movimientos bruscos."

# game/episode014.rpy:927
translate spanish uailea_tand_926b73f9:

#   c "We're not here to harm you, we just want a word with Nkoy Rhedia."
    c "No estamos aquí para hacerte daño, sólo queremos hablar con Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode014.rpy:930
translate spanish uailea_tand_ddb41974:

#   woman "Who sent you?"
    woman "¿Quién te envía?"

# game/episode014.rpy:932
translate spanish uailea_tand_2218205f:

#   zi "The Council of Nkoy."
    zi "El Consejo de Nkoy."

# game/episode014.rpy:934
translate spanish uailea_tand_764cd288:

#   "One of the women spat at Ziv, but luckily missed her mark, because Aven yanked her away."
    "Una de las mujeres escupió a Ziv, pero por suerte no dio en el blanco, porque Aven la apartó de un tirón."

# game/episode014.rpy:936
translate spanish uailea_tand_5025427c:

#   av "None of that, or we'll be forced to gag you."
    av "Nada de eso, o nos veremos obligados a amordazarte."

# game/episode014.rpy:937
translate spanish uailea_tand_ed7c31f3:

#   woman "We have nothing to say to Council lapdogs."
    woman "No tenemos nada que decir a los perritos falderos del Consejo."

# game/episode014.rpy:938
translate spanish uailea_tand_3d85a12a:

#   c "Well, we're not."
    c "Pues no."

# game/episode014.rpy:939
translate spanish uailea_tand_93c0ae76:

#   c "I'm not sure what the Council's next move will be, but I doubt it will be peaceful negotiations."
    c "No estoy seguro de cuál será el próximo movimiento del Consejo, pero dudo que sean negociaciones pacíficas."

# game/episode014.rpy:940
translate spanish uailea_tand_c7397861:

#   c "We were sent to talk to you and find a way out of this mess."
    c "Nos enviaron para hablar contigo y encontrar una salida a este lío."

# game/episode014.rpy:941
translate spanish uailea_tand_5b557f77:

#   c "If you'd rather wait for the cavalry to level this place, be my guest."
    c "Si prefieres esperar a la caballería para arrasar este lugar, adelante."

# game/episode014.rpy:943
translate spanish uailea_tand_9d0b113c:

#   "The prisoners were silently glaring at me."
    "Los prisioneros me miraban en silencio."

# game/episode014.rpy:944
translate spanish uailea_tand_d1849364:

#   c "I'd very much like to do this the non-violent way, but traipsing through this forest with a string of prisoners isn't what I had in mind, to be honest."
    c "Me gustaría mucho hacer esto de forma no violenta, pero atravesar este bosque con una serie de prisioneros no es lo que tenía en mente, para ser honesto."

# game/episode014.rpy:945
translate spanish uailea_tand_5c7de20d:

#   c "You're obviously out of your depth here swinging a gun and playing soldier."
    c "Obviamente estás fuera de ti aquí blandiendo un arma y jugando a ser soldado."

# game/episode014.rpy:946
translate spanish uailea_tand_d6882da9:

#   c "I just want to speak to Rhedia and I promise not to hurt her in any way."
    c "Sólo quiero hablar con Rhedia y prometo no hacerle ningún daño."

# game/episode014.rpy:948
translate spanish uailea_tand_fbb63a66:

#   woman "What guarantees do we have?"
    woman "¿Qué garantías tenemos?"

# game/episode014.rpy:949
translate spanish uailea_tand_eded71d8:

#   c "None."
    c "Ninguna."

# game/episode014.rpy:950
translate spanish uailea_tand_49617de0:

#   c "But you have my word, and that's got to be enough."
    c "Pero tienes mi palabra, y eso tiene que ser suficiente."

# game/episode014.rpy:951
translate spanish uailea_tand_ba6a23e9:

#   "The prisoners looked at each other, and I spotted a hint of resignation."
    "Los prisioneros se miraron entre sí y percibí un atisbo de resignación."

# game/episode014.rpy:952
translate spanish uailea_tand_7ed5a8b1:

#   woman "Very well, we'll take you to our camp."
    woman "Muy bien, te llevaremos a nuestro campamento."

# game/episode014.rpy:954
translate spanish uailea_tand_ce8f6f80:

#   "We made the prisoners walk in front of us."
    "Hicimos que los prisioneros caminaran delante de nosotros."

# game/episode014.rpy:955
translate spanish uailea_tand_5b060a9f:

#   "Apparently, there weren't any other sentries on this side of the encampment."
    "Al parecer, no había otros centinelas en este lado del campamento."

# game/episode014.rpy:957
translate spanish uailea_tand_864bebab:

#   "The bustle of the camp could be heard easily in the distance, nobody made much effort to conceal their presence."
